{"type":"message","id":"9b273f55","parentId":"92bfe6e5","timestamp":"2026-04-21T15:41:37.328Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_p4arztoi9lm4_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Memory - 2026-04-21\n\n## DTLX Dashboard - Sidebar Fix (Session 2026-04-20)\n\n### Problem\n4 layout bugs reported by user:\n1. Sidebar bị \"trôi\" khi cuộn trang\n2. Content lấn sang trái (đè Sidebar)\n3. Header/Sidebar không đồng bộ\n4. Tooltip/Dropdown lệch tọa độ\n\n### Root Cause\nSidebar nằm trong `.main-area` có `overflow-y: auto` → cuộn theo content.\nTemplate có `.page-content { margin-left: var(--bs-sidenav-width) }` nhưng không đủ.\n\n### Final Fix (CSS only)\n**AdminLayout.jsx** structure:\n- `.sidenav-menu` → `position: fixed; left: 0; top: 0; height: 100vh; z-index: 100; overflow-y: auto`\n- `.main-area` → `padding-left: 240px; height: 100vh; overflow-y: auto; transition: padding-left 0.3s ease`\n\n**index.css** additions:\n- Condensed: `padding-left: 72px`\n- Expanded: `padding-left: 240px`\n- Logo area inside `.main-area` (not inside sidebar)\n\n### Git Workflow\n1. `git checkout develop && git pull`\n2. `git checkout feat/cms-driving-training-design`\n3. `git merge develop`\n4. `git push`\n5. User tạo MR thủ công: https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-frontend/-/merge_requests/new?source_branch=feat/cms-driving-training-design\n\n### Key Files Modified (DTLX Frontend)\n- `src/layouts/AdminLayout.jsx` - structure\n- `src/index.css` - sidebar + main-area CSS\n\n### VPS Services\n- DTLX Frontend: http://103.253.21.139:3002 (running)\n- DTLX Backend: http://103.253.21.139:5555 (running)\n- MAIY Frontend: http://103.253.21.139:3000 (running - DO NOT STOP)\n- MAIY Backend: http://103.253.21.139:4000 (running)\n\n### DTLX Login Issue\n- Backend database appears empty (no users)\n- Login credentials don't work\n- `admin123@gmail.com` / `123456` fails\n- MongoDB `dtlx-mongo` container at port 27017\n\n## AHV QLHV Project Setup (03:29 UTC)\n\n### Repositories Cloned\n- **Frontend:** `ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-fe` → `workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe`\n- **Backend:** `ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be` → `workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be`\n- Branch: `develop`\n- Latest FE commit: `18af43d` (Merge fix/conflix, Apr 20)\n- Latest BE commit: `aa5f3b2` (Merge fix/conflict, Apr 20)\n\n### Tech Stack\n- **Frontend:** Next.js (src/ directory)\n- **Backend:** Node.js/TypeScript (src/ directory)\n- **Database:** MongoDB\n\n### Next Steps\n- Install dependencies\n- Configure environment\n- Run services\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776786097298}}
{"type":"message","id":"70916871","parentId":"9b273f55","timestamp":"2026-04-21T15:41:42.216Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hey, checking in. The user seems to be checking in from openclaw-tui. I see from memory we have a lot of active projects. Let me keep it simple and check in.","thinkingSignature":"7eb99c70f26acdde7cf05d70eae77effeb534e4b5bb57956a3f649b4d62dfb71"},{"type":"text","text":"Chào! 👋\n\nĐang có vài thứ đang chạy:\n\n- **DTLX CMS** — http://103.253.21.139:3002 (frontend) + :5555 (backend) — cái sidebar fix mới xong\n- **MAIY Tech Hub** — http://103.253.21.139:3000 (frontend) + :4000 (backend)\n- **AHV QLHV** — vừa clone xong, chưa setup\n\nCó gì cần làm không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":2837,"output":165,"cacheRead":8383,"cacheWrite":156,"totalTokens":11541,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776786097330,"responseId":"0636cdb16ad95e71551fa997aa9f40e9"}}
