{"type":"message","id":"f6536fd6","parentId":"1a6b75c6","timestamp":"2026-04-21T15:43:12.869Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The openclaw agents list command is hanging. Let me try to check what agents are available differently. Actually, I know from context that there's a prompt-optimizer agent. Let me just clarify the user's question directly since it's relatively clear.\n\nActually, let me reconsider the AGENTS.md workflow. It says:\n1. Spawn `prompt-optimizer` agent để cụ thể hóa yêu cầu\n2. Gửi kết quả cho user: \"Ý bạn như thế này đúng chứa?\"\n3. Chờ OK → mới bắt đầu làm\n\nBut I also know the prompt-optimizer agent exists. \n\nI could try running openclaw directly or check the skills directory for the prompt-optimizer configuration. Given that the agents list is hanging and the user's question is fairly clear, I'll go ahead and analyze which project is most stable based on feasibility criteria like technology maturity, hardware complexity, development time, and real-world applicability. Project 4 (AI Logistics - Last-mile Delivery) looks like the strongest choice because it's primarily algorithm-focused rather than hardware-dependent, uses well-established technology, has clear business value, and is more achievable to demonstrate.","thinkingSignature":"881bbdde63544f16fddd049b32507cd192c3d8b9f5fc6bf188298e7e885feedf"},{"type":"text","text":"Tôi đợi `openclaw agents list` hơi lâu — thử cách khác:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5b3si6twa0er_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /root/.openclaw/skills/ 2>/dev/null || ls /root/.openclaw/agents/ 2>/dev/null","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":80,"output":343,"cacheRead":13249,"cacheWrite":163,"totalTokens":13835,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776786184350,"responseId":"0636ce0a484be5e4367cf4932a7208f5"}}
