{"type":"message","id":"d5ee4b9e","parentId":"46568ba6","timestamp":"2026-04-21T16:12:08.917Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create a README with setup instructions.","thinkingSignature":"acc3fce7b63fc0c78fcf121694fff8f8e6ffe06d649dd5b18771d31b4b6798b7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1z611p00joky_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/README.md","content":"# S1 PPE Safety Monitor — Demo\n\n> Hệ thống AI Giám sát và Cảnh báo An toàn Lao động tại Công trường\n> Computer Vision + Deep Learning (YOLOv8) + Real-time Dashboard\n\n## 🏗️ Architecture\n\n```\nCamera/Video → Flask Backend (YOLOv8) → Socket.IO → React Dashboard\n                      ↓\n                  MongoDB (alerts)\n```\n\n## 📁 Structure\n\n```\ns1-ppe-safety/\n├── backend/\n│   ├── app.py              # Flask + Socket.IO API\n│   ├── detector.py         # YOLOv8 detection engine\n│   ├── video_processor.py  # Video file / webcam processor\n│   ├── requirements.txt\n│   ├── .env.example\n│   └── Dockerfile.backend\n├── frontend/\n│   ├── src/\n│   │   ├── App.jsx         # Dashboard (Ant Design)\n│   │   └── main.jsx\n│   ├── package.json\n│   └── vite.config.js\n└── devops/\n    ├── Dockerfile.backend\n    └── docker-compose.yml\n```\n\n## ⚡ Quick Start\n\n### 1. Prerequisites\n\n- Python 3.11+\n- Node.js 18+\n- MongoDB (user-provided, see below)\n\n### 2. Backend\n\n```bash\ncd backend\n\n# Create venv\npython3 -m venv venv\nsource venv/bin/activate\n\n# Install\npip install -r requirements.txt\n\n# Download YOLOv8 model\npython -c \"from ultralytics import YOLO; YOLO('yolov8n.pt')\"\n\n# Copy env\ncp .env.example .env\n# Edit .env → set MONGO_URI to your MongoDB\n\n# Run\npython app.py\n# → http://localhost:5000\n```\n\n### 3. Frontend\n\n```bash\ncd frontend\n\nnpm install\nnpm run dev\n# → http://localhost:3003\n```\n\n### 4. Docker (optional)\n\n```bash\ncd devops\ndocker-compose up --build\n```\n\n## 🔑 Configuration\n\n### MongoDB (user provides)\n\nUser cần cung cấp MongoDB URI. Set trong `backend/.env`:\n\n```\nMONGO_URI=mongodb://<host>:<port>/ppe_safety\nMONGO_DB=ppe_safety\n```\n\nHoặc dùng Docker MongoDB:\n\n```bash\ndocker run -d -p 27018:27017 --name ppe-mongo mongo:7\n# → MONGO_URI=mongodb://localhost:27018\n```\n\n### Video Demo\n\nĐặt file video vào `backend/demo.mp4`. Video nên chứa:\n- Người đội mũ bảo hộ màu vàng/cam\n- Người mặc áo phản quang\n- Mix cả người có và không có PPE\n\nVideo mẫu có thể tải từ:\n- YouTube: \"construction site safety\" footage\n- Pexels / Pixabay: free stock videos\n\n## 📡 API Endpoints\n\n| Method | Endpoint | Mô tả |\n|--------|----------|-------|\n| GET | `/health` | Health check |\n| POST | `/api/start` | Start video processor |\n| POST | `/api/stop` | Stop video processor |\n| GET | `/api/summary` | Get latest detection summary |\n| POST | `/api/detect` | Detect PPE from base64 image |\n| GET | `/api/alerts?limit=50` | Get recent alerts |\n| GET | `/api/alerts/stats` | Get 24h alert statistics |\n\n## 🔌 WebSocket Events\n\n| Event | Direction | Payload |\n|-------|-----------|---------|\n| `ppe_alert` | Server → Client | Violation alert |\n| `detection_summary` | Server → Client | Summary update |\n| `subscribe` | Client → Server | Subscribe to camera |\n\n## 🎯 PPE Classes\n\n| Class | Mô tả | Detection |\n|-------|-------|-----------|\n| `helmet` | Mũ bảo hộ | Color analysis (yellow/orange HSV) |\n| `safety-vest` | Áo phản quang | Bright color + reflective detection |\n| `no-helmet` | Vi phạm: không đội mũ | Rule-based from helmet detection |\n| `no-vest` | Vi phạm: không mặc áo | Rule-based from vest detection |\n\n## 🚀 Production Deployment\n\n1. Thay YOLOv8n → YOLOv8s hoặc fine-tuned PPE model\n2. Cấu hình nginx reverse proxy (HTTPS)\n3. GPU inference cho camera nhiều người\n4. Alert notification (email/SMS/Telegram)\n5. Multi-camera management\n\n## 📊 Compliance Score Logic\n\n```\ncompliance_rate = (compliant / total_persons) × 100%\n\n🟢 >= 80%  : An toàn\n🟡 50-80%  : Cảnh báo\n🔴 < 50%   : Nguy hiểm\n```\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":75,"output":1163,"cacheRead":42726,"cacheWrite":704,"totalTokens":44668,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776787911545,"responseId":"0636d4c8a91a681a9790d8ce533ee192"}}
