{"type":"message","id":"a10e5acd","parentId":"336ffadc","timestamp":"2026-04-21T16:58:29.960Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0tm83s4tq3vl_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n    \"detections\": [\n        {\n            \"bbox\": [\n                776.0,\n                302.0,\n                942.0,\n                680.0\n            ],\n            \"center_x\": 859.0,\n            \"center_y\": 491.0,\n            \"class_id\": 0,\n            \"class_name\": \"person\",\n            \"confidence\": 0.92,\n            \"height\": 378.0,\n            \"ppe_status\": {\n                \"compliant\": true,\n                \"has_helmet\": true,\n                \"has_vest\": true\n            },\n            \"width\": 166.0\n        },\n        {\n            \"bbox\": [\n                230.0,"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":92,"aggregated":"{\n    \"detections\": [\n        {\n            \"bbox\": [\n                776.0,\n                302.0,\n                942.0,\n                680.0\n            ],\n            \"center_x\": 859.0,\n            \"center_y\": 491.0,\n            \"class_id\": 0,\n            \"class_name\": \"person\",\n            \"confidence\": 0.92,\n            \"height\": 378.0,\n            \"ppe_status\": {\n                \"compliant\": true,\n                \"has_helmet\": true,\n                \"has_vest\": true\n            },\n            \"width\": 166.0\n        },\n        {\n            \"bbox\": [\n                230.0,","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776790709945}}
{"type":"message","id":"d06ec3e1","parentId":"a10e5acd","timestamp":"2026-04-21T16:58:36.672Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The system is working well. Let me give the user a summary.","thinkingSignature":"92d792b7f1b316724360f35e024ece9cacfeefbe61ff64d7bf02e51543fd1070"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ Hoàn thành!\n\n**Cập nhật dashboard:**\n\n- Giờ hiển thị **ảnh thực từ video** với bounding boxes vẽ sẵn từ backend\n- Poll 500ms/lần → frames chuyển động mượt\n- HUD hiển thị số liệu trực tiếp trên video\n\n### 🔗 Truy cập\n\n- **Dashboard:** http://103.253.21.139:3003\n- **Backend:** http://103.253.21.139:5000\n\n### 📊 Đang chạy\n\n```\nVideo: 15s loop, 1280x720\nDetection: Edge+Blob+Color (CPU)\nTốc độ: 2 fps\n```\n\nVào dashboard xem video với bounding boxes nhé! 🎥"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":197,"output":215,"cacheRead":114769,"cacheWrite":280,"totalTokens":115461,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776790709969,"responseId":"0636dfb7d807193eb4e8481758223c2b"}}
