{"type":"message","id":"90eaca2e","parentId":"8c204563","timestamp":"2026-04-21T17:00:34.683Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-04-21 16:56:58 UTC] Exec completed (sharp-sh, code 0) :: 1-ppe-safety/frontend/node_modules/rollup/dist/es/shared/node-entry.js:17817:29) at ModuleScope.findVariable (file:///root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/frontend/no…\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-21 17:00 UTC] hiển thị thẳng video luôn nhé không dùng frame như này, video thực tế nhìn người thật thì mới có thể giám sát"}],"timestamp":1776790834661}}
{"type":"message","id":"37cdfdef","parentId":"90eaca2e","timestamp":"2026-04-21T17:01:26.710Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to display the actual video directly (using HTML5 video element) instead of polling individual frames. They want to see real people in real video footage so they can actually monitor. This makes total sense - the current approach of rendering annotated frames as images is a workaround, not a proper video player.\n\nThe solution is:\n1. Frontend: Use HTML5 `<video>` element to play the video directly\n2. Overlay detection bounding boxes using absolute positioned divs or canvas on top\n3. Backend: Keep providing detection data via WebSocket/Socket.IO or polling\n4. The video file should be served statically or streamed\n\nLet me implement this properly:\n\n\nI'll set up the backend to serve the video file statically so the frontend can access it directly, then sync the bounding box overlays with the video playback using the `/api/summary` endpoint to get detection data. For now I'll skip the frame-accurate synchronization since our detection runs at 2fps and just focus on getting the video playing smoothly with boxes overlaid.","thinkingSignature":"0997c2db100e14018a2e28ed0eeba05d1258b35c23debf964733d1db46a51a07"},{"type":"text","text":"Hiểu rồi — hiển thị video thực bằng HTML5 `<video>`, bounding boxes overlay bằng canvas phía trên:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_np2eb4cayi7u_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/frontend/src/App.jsx","content":"import { useState, useEffect, useRef } from 'react'\nimport { io } from 'socket.io-client'\nimport {\n  Layout, Card, Row, Col, Statistic, Tag, Badge,\n  Button, Space, Typography, Alert, Progress, List, Tooltip\n} from 'antd'\nimport {\n  SafetyOutlined, AlertOutlined, UserOutlined,\n  CheckCircleOutlined, StopOutlined, PlayCircleOutlined,\n  VideoCameraOutlined, ReloadOutlined, CameraOutlined, LoadingOutlined\n} from '@ant-design/icons'\n\nconst { Header, Content, Sider } = Layout\nconst { Title, Text } = Typography\n\nconst API_BASE = import.meta.env.VITE_API_BASE || ''\nconst VIDEO_URL = `${API_BASE}/video/demo.mp4`\n\nasync function fetchAPI(path) {\n  const res = await fetch(`${API_BASE}${path}`)\n  if (!res.ok) throw new Error(`${path} → ${res.status}`)\n  return res.json()\n}\n\nfunction StatsCard({ title, value, icon, color, sub }) {\n  return (\n    <Card size=\"small\" style={{ borderRadius: 12 }}>\n      <Statistic\n        title={<Text type=\"secondary\" style={{ fontSize: 13 }}>{title}</Text>}\n        value={value}\n        valueStyle={{ color, fontSize: 28, fontWeight: 700 }}\n        prefix={<span style={{ marginRight: 8 }}>{icon}</span>}\n      />\n      {sub && <div style={{ marginTop: 4, fontSize: 12, color: '#888' }}>{sub}</div>}\n    </Card>\n  )\n}\n\nfunction AlertItem({ alert }) {\n  const d = alert.detection || {}\n  const isViolation = !d.compliant\n  return (\n    <List.Item style={{ padding: '8px 0' }}>\n      <Space align=\"start\" style={{ width: '100%' }}>\n        <Badge status={isViolation ? 'error' : 'success'} />\n        <div style={{ flex: 1 }}>\n          <Space>\n            {d.has_helmet === false && <Tag color=\"red\">NO HELMET</Tag>}\n            {d.has_vest === false && <Tag color=\"orange\">NO VEST</Tag>}\n            {d.compliant && <Tag color=\"green\">OK</Tag>}\n          </Space>\n          <div style={{ fontSize: 11, color: '#999', marginTop: 2 }}>\n            {alert.timestamp ? new Date(alert.timestamp).toLocaleTimeString() : '—'}\n            {' · conf: '}{d.confidence?.toFixed(2) || '—'}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </Space>\n    </List.Item>\n  )\n}\n\n// ── Video Player with Detection Overlay ──────────────────────────────────────\nfunction VideoPlayer({ onSummaryUpdate }) {\n  const videoRef = useRef(null)\n  const canvasRef = useRef(null)\n  const [detections, setDetections] = useState([])\n  const [summary, setSummary] = useState(null)\n  const [videoReady, setVideoReady] = useState(false)\n  const [videoError, setVideoError] = useState(null)\n  const [lastUpdate, setLastUpdate] = useState(null)\n  const [playing, setPlaying] = useState(false)\n  const animationRef = useRef(null)\n\n  // ── Draw boxes on canvas overlay ─────────────────────────────────────────\n  const drawDetections = useRef(null)\n\n  // ── Sync detections with video ────────────────────────────────────────────\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const video = videoRef.current\n    const canvas = canvasRef.current\n    if (!video || !canvas) return\n\n    const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d')\n\n    const draw = () => {\n      if (!video || !ctx) return\n\n      // Match canvas size to video display size\n      const vw = video.offsetWidth || 640\n      const vh = video.offsetHeight || 360\n\n      if (canvas.width !== vw || canvas.height !== vh) {\n        canvas.width = vw\n        canvas.height = vh\n      }\n\n      ctx.clearRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height)\n\n      const s = summary || {}\n      const dets = detections || []\n\n      // Scale factors (video is 1280x720)\n      const scaleX = canvas.width / 1280\n      const scaleY = canvas.height / 720\n\n      dets.forEach(d => {\n        const [x1, y1, x2, y2] = d.bbox\n        const sx1 = x1 * scaleX, sy1 = y1 * scaleY\n        const sx2 = x2 * scaleX, sy2 = y2 * scaleY\n        const sw = sx2 - sx1, sh = sy2 - sy1\n        const ppe = d.ppe_status\n\n        const color = ppe.compliant ? '#00c853' : '#ff1744'\n\n        // Box\n        ctx.strokeStyle = color\n        ctx.lineWidth = 2\n        ctx.strokeRect(sx1, sy1, sw, sh)\n\n        // Fill\n        ctx.fillStyle = ppe.compliant\n          ? 'rgba(0,200,83,0.12)'\n          : 'rgba(255,23,68,0.18)'\n        ctx.fillRect(sx1, sy1, sw, sh)\n\n        // Label\n        const label = ppe.compliant\n          ? 'OK'\n          : `${!ppe.has_helmet ? 'NO-HELMET' : ''} ${!ppe.has_vest ? 'NO-VEST' : ''}`.trim()\n        ctx.fillStyle = color\n        ctx.font = 'bold 11px monospace'\n        const tw = ctx.measureText(label).width\n        ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)'\n        ctx.fillRect(sx1, sy1 - 18, tw + 8, 17)\n        ctx.fillStyle = color\n        ctx.fillText(label, sx1 + 4, sy1 - 5)\n      })\n\n      animationRef.current = requestAnimationFrame(draw)\n    }\n\n    // Poll summary + detections\n    const poll = setInterval(async () => {\n      try {\n        const data = await fetchAPI('/api/summary')\n        if (data.summary) {\n          setSummary(data.summary)\n          onSummaryUpdate?.(data.summary)\n        }\n        if (data.detections) {\n          setDetections(data.detections)\n        }\n        setLastUpdate(new Date().toLocaleTimeString())\n      } catch {}\n    }, 500)\n\n    draw()\n\n    return () => {\n      clearInterval(poll)\n      if (animationRef.current) cancelAnimationFrame(animationRef.current)\n    }\n  }, [summary, detections])\n\n  const complianceColor = summary\n    ? (summary.compliance_rate >= 80 ? '#52c41a'\n      : summary.compliance_rate >= 50 ? '#faad14' : '#ff4d4f')\n    : '#888'\n\n  return (\n    <div style={{ position: 'relative', borderRadius: 12, overflow: 'hidden', background: '#000' }}>\n      {/* HTML5 Video */}\n      <div style={{ position: 'relative', lineHeight: 0 }}>\n        <video\n          ref={videoRef}\n          src={VIDEO_URL}\n          controls\n          autoPlay\n          loop\n          muted\n          playsInline\n          style={{\n            width: '100%',\n            display: 'block',\n            background: '#000',\n          }}\n          onCanPlay={() => setVideoReady(true)}\n          onError={(e) => setVideoError('Không thể tải video')}\n          onPlay={() => setPlaying(true)}\n          onPause={() => setPlaying(false)}\n        />\n\n        {/* Canvas overlay for bounding boxes */}\n        <canvas\n          ref={canvasRef}\n          style={{\n            position: 'absolute',\n            top: 0,\n            left: 0,\n            width: '100%',\n            height: '100%',\n            pointerEvents: 'none',\n          }}\n        />\n      </div>\n\n      {/* HUD — top right */}\n      <div style={{\n        position: 'absolute', top: 12, right: 12,\n        background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.72)',\n        borderRadius: 6, padding: '6px 12px',\n        fontSize: 11, color: '#0f0',\n        fontFamily: 'monospace',\n      }}>\n        {playing ? '● LIVE' : '⏸ PAUSED'} · Edge+Blob\n      </div>\n\n      {/* HUD — top left */}\n      <div style={{\n        position: 'absolute', top: 12, left: 12,\n        background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.6)',\n        borderRadius: 6, padding: '4px 10px',\n        fontSize: 10, color: '#aaa',\n        fontFamily: 'monospace',\n      }}>\n        Cập nhật: {lastUpdate || '...'}\n      </div>\n\n      {/* HUD — bottom left stats */}\n      {summary && (\n        <div style={{\n          position: 'absolute', bottom: 12, left: 12,\n          background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.75)',\n          borderRadius: 8, padding: '10px 14px',\n          fontFamily: 'monospace', fontSize: 12,\n        }}>\n          <div style={{ color: '#fff', marginBottom: 4 }}>\n            👤 {summary.total_persons || 0} phát hiện\n          </div>\n          <div style={{ color: '#52c41a' }}>\n            ✅ Tuân thủ: {summary.compliant || 0}\n          </div>\n          <div style={{ color: '#ff4d4f' }}>\n            ❌ Vi phạm: {summary.violations || 0}\n          </div>\n          <div style={{ color: complianceColor, marginTop: 4 }}>\n            📊 Tỷ lệ: {summary.compliance_rate || 0}%\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* Error / Loading state */}\n      {videoError && (\n        <div style={{\n          position: 'absolute', inset: 0,\n          display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center',\n          background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.8)', color: '#ff4d4f',\n        }}>\n          {videoError}\n        </div>\n      )}\n      {!videoReady && !videoError && (\n        <div style={{\n          position: 'absolute', inset: 0,\n          display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center',\n          background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)', color: '#aaa',\n          flexDirection: 'column', gap: 8,\n        }}>\n          <LoadingOutlined style={{ fontSize: 32 }} />\n          <span>Đang tải video...</span>\n        </div>\n      )}\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n\n// ── Main App ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nexport default function App() {\n  const [summary, setSummary] = useState({\n    total_persons: 0, compliant: 0, violations: 0,\n    no_helmet: 0, no_vest: 0, compliance_rate: 100,\n  })\n  const [alerts, setAlerts] = useState([])\n  const [status, setStatus] = useState('connecting')\n  const [alertStats, setAlertStats] = useState({})\n  const socketRef = useRef(null)\n\n  // ── Socket.IO ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const socket = io(API_BASE || window.location.origin, {\n      transports: ['websocket', 'polling'],\n      reconnectionAttempts: 5,\n      reconnectionDelay: 2000,\n    })\n    socketRef.current = socket\n\n    socket.on('connect', () => {\n      socket.emit('subscribe', { camera_id: 'demo-camera' })\n      setStatus('live')\n    })\n    socket.on('disconnect', () => setStatus('stopped'))\n    socket.on('detection_summary', (data) => {\n      if (data.summary) setSummary(data.summary)\n    })\n    socket.on('ppe_alert', (alert) => {\n      setAlerts(prev => [alert, ...prev].slice(0, 100))\n      try {\n        const audio = new Audio(\n          'data:audio/wav;base64,'\n        )\n        audio.volume = 0.3\n        audio.play().catch(() => {})\n      } catch {}\n    })\n    return () => socket.disconnect()\n  }, [])\n\n  // ── Poll alerts ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const loadAlerts = async () => {\n      try {\n        const [alertsData, statsData] = await Promise.all([\n          fetchAPI('/api/alerts?limit=20'),\n          fetchAPI('/api/alerts/stats').catch(() => ({})),\n        ])\n        if (Array.isArray(alertsData)) setAlerts(alertsData)\n        if (statsData && !statsData.error) setAlertStats(statsData)\n      } catch {}\n    }\n    loadAlerts()\n    const interval = setInterval(loadAlerts, 10000)\n    return () => clearInterval(interval)\n  }, [])\n\n  const complianceColor = summary.compliance_rate >= 80 ? '#52c41a'\n    : summary.compliance_rate >= 50 ? '#faad14' : '#ff4d4f'\n\n  return (\n    <Layout style={{ minHeight: '100vh', background: '#0f0f1a' }}>\n      {/* Header */}\n      <Header style={{\n        background: '#1a1a2e',\n        borderBottom: '1px solid #2a2a4a',\n        display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'space-between',\n        padding: '0 24px',\n      }}>\n        <Space>\n          <SafetyOutlined style={{ fontSize: 24, color: '#faad14' }} />\n          <Title level={4} style={{ color: '#fff', margin: 0 }}>\n            PPE Safety Monitor\n          </Title>\n          <Badge\n            status={status === 'live' ? 'processing' : 'error'}\n            text={<Text style={{ color: status === 'live' ? '#52c41a' : '#ff4d4f', fontSize: 12 }}>\n              {status === 'live' ? 'LIVE' : 'CONNECTING'}\n            </Text>}\n          />\n        </Space>\n        <Space>\n          <Tooltip title=\"Reload alerts\">\n            <Button\n              icon={<ReloadOutlined />}\n              onClick={() => fetchAPI('/api/alerts?limit=20').then(d => Array.isArray(d) && setAlerts(d))}\n            >\n              Reload\n            </Button>\n          </Tooltip>\n          <Tag icon={<CameraOutlined />} style={{ background: '#16213e', border: 'none', color: '#aaa' }}>\n            Demo Video\n          </Tag>\n        </Space>\n      </Header>\n\n      <Layout>\n        <Content style={{ padding: 20, background: '#0f0f1a' }}>\n          {/* Stats Row */}\n          <Row gutter={[16, 16]} style={{ marginBottom: 20 }}>\n            <Col xs={24} sm={12} md={6}>\n              <StatsCard\n                title=\"Tổng người phát hiện\"\n                value={summary.total_persons}\n                icon={<UserOutlined />}\n                color=\"#1890ff\"\n              />\n            </Col>\n            <Col xs={24} sm={12} md={6}>\n              <StatsCard\n                title=\"Tuân thủ (✓)\"\n                value={summary.compliant}\n                icon={<CheckCircleOutlined />}\n                color=\"#52c41a\"\n              />\n            </Col>\n            <Col xs={24} sm={12} md={6}>\n              <StatsCard\n                title=\"Vi phạm (✗)\"\n                value={summary.violations}\n                icon={<StopOutlined />}\n                color=\"#ff4d4f\"\n                sub={summary.no_helmet > 0 ? `• Không mũ: ${summary.no_helmet}` : null}\n              />\n            </Col>\n            <Col xs={24} sm={12} md={6}>\n              <Card size=\"small\" style={{ borderRadius: 12 }}>\n                <Statistic\n                  title={<Text type=\"secondary\" style={{ fontSize: 13 }}>Tỷ lệ tuân thủ</Text>}\n                  value={summary.compliance_rate}\n                  suffix=\"%\"\n                  valueStyle={{ color: complianceColor, fontSize: 28, fontWeight: 700 }}\n                  prefix={<SafetyOutlined style={{ marginRight: 8 }} />}\n                />\n                <Progress\n                  percent={summary.compliance_rate}\n                  showInfo={false}\n                  strokeColor={complianceColor}\n                  style={{ marginTop: 8 }}\n                />\n              </Card>\n            </Col>\n          </Row>\n\n          {/* Video + Alert Panel */}\n          <Row gutter={[16, 16]}>\n            <Col xs={24} lg={14}>\n              <Card\n                title={\n                  <Space>\n                    <VideoCameraOutlined />\n                    Camera Feed — Demo\n                  </Space>\n                }\n                style={{ background: '#1a1a2e', border: '1px solid #2a2a4a' }}\n                styles={{ header: { color: '#fff', borderBottom: '1px solid #2a2a4a' } }}\n              >\n                <VideoPlayer onSummaryUpdate={setSummary} />\n                <Alert\n                  message=\"Video thực tế. Bounding boxes hiển thị vị trí phát hiện người và trạng thái PPE.\"\n                  type=\"info\"\n                  showIcon\n                  style={{ marginTop: 12 }}\n                />\n              </Card>\n            </Col>\n\n            <Col xs={24} lg={10}>\n              <Card\n                title={\n                  <Space>\n                    <AlertOutlined style={{ color: '#ff4d4f' }} />\n                    Cảnh báo thời gian thực\n                    <Badge count={alerts.length} style={{ backgroundColor: '#ff4d4f' }} />\n                  </Space>\n                }\n                style={{ background: '#1a1a2e', border: '1px solid #2a2a4a', height: '100%' }}\n                styles={{ header: { color: '#fff', borderBottom: '1px solid #2a2a4a' } }}\n                bodyStyle={{ maxHeight: 500, overflow: 'auto' }}\n              >\n                {alerts.length === 0 ? (\n                  <div style={{ textAlign: 'center', padding: 40, color: '#555' }}>\n                    <SafetyOutlined style={{ fontSize: 48, marginBottom: 12 }} />\n                    <div>Không có cảnh báo nào</div>\n                    <div style={{ fontSize: 12, marginTop: 4 }}>Hệ thống đang hoạt động bình thường</div>\n                  </div>\n                ) : (\n                  <List\n                    dataSource={alerts}\n                    renderItem={(item) => <AlertItem alert={item} />}\n                    locale={{ emptyText: 'Không có cảnh báo' }}\n                  />\n                )}\n              </Card>\n            </Col>\n          </Row>\n        </Content>\n\n        {/* Sidebar */}\n        <Sider\n          width={240}\n          style={{ background: '#1a1a2e', borderLeft: '1px solid #2a2a4a', padding: 16 }}\n        >\n          <Title level={5} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>Thống kê 24h</Title>\n          <Space direction=\"vertical\" style={{ width: '100%' }} size={12}>\n            <Card size=\"small\" style={{ background: '#16213e' }}>\n              <Statistic\n                title={<Text style={{ color: '#aaa', fontSize: 12 }}>Tổng cảnh báo</Text>}\n                value={alertStats.total || alerts.length}\n                valueStyle={{ color: '#fff', fontSize: 24 }}\n              />\n            </Card>\n            <Card size=\"small\" style={{ background: '#16213e' }}>\n              <Statistic\n                title={<Text style={{ color: '#aaa', fontSize: 12 }}>Không đội mũ</Text>}\n                value={alertStats.no_helmet || 0}\n                valueStyle={{ color: '#ff4d4f', fontSize: 24 }}\n              />\n            </Card>\n            <Card size=\"small\" style={{ background: '#16213e' }}>\n              <Statistic\n                title={<Text style={{ color: '#aaa', fontSize: 12 }}>Không áo phản quang</Text>}\n                value={alertStats.no_vest || 0}\n                valueStyle={{ color: '#faad14', fontSize: 24 }}\n              />\n            </Card>\n\n            <div style={{ marginTop: 16 }}>\n              <Title level={5} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>Camera</Title>\n              <Card size=\"small\" style={{ background: '#16213e' }}>\n                <Space>\n                  <Badge status=\"success\" />\n                  <Text style={{ color: '#aaa', fontSize: 13 }}>demo-camera</Text>\n                </Space>\n                <div style={{ fontSize: 11, color: '#666', marginTop: 4 }}>1280×720 · Edge+Blob</div>\n              </Card>\n            </div>\n          </Space>\n        </Sider>\n      </Layout>\n    </Layout>\n  )\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":5323,"cacheRead":113550,"cacheWrite":506,"totalTokens":119379,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776790834683,"responseId":"0636e0340449cf27aa968bf251acb1e5"}}
