{"type":"message","id":"6f11b209","parentId":"976d379d","timestamp":"2026-04-21T17:13:35.102Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-21 17:13 UTC] camera thực vẫn báo lỗi tair video, phần camera thưực không cần hiển thị bounding boxes + overlayboxes chỉ để quan sát còn frame bên duươới moơới để giám sát"}],"timestamp":1776791615082}}
{"type":"message","id":"9e9c583b","parentId":"6f11b209","timestamp":"2026-04-21T17:14:04.934Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says:\n1. The real video still shows \"loading video\" error\n2. They don't need bounding boxes overlay on the real video - just show the plain video for observation\n3. The annotated frame below is for monitoring/surveillance purposes\n\nSo the layout should be:\n- TOP: Plain real video (no canvas overlay, no bounding boxes) - just for viewing\n- BOTTOM: Annotated frame with bounding boxes from backend - for surveillance/monitoring\n\nLet me simplify the VideoPlayer to just show the plain video, and keep the AnnotatedFrame with the detection boxes.","thinkingSignature":"dd6920db963176a188d76d7972a00af4d7bac8186e78d335c591c114b3833c69"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s4w0j6o5uqxm_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/frontend/src/App.jsx","edits":[{"oldText":"// ── Video Player ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction VideoPlayer({ onSummaryUpdate }) {\n  const videoRef = useRef(null)\n  const canvasRef = useRef(null)\n  const [detections, setDetections] = useState([])\n  const [summary, setSummary] = useState(null)\n  const [videoReady, setVideoReady] = useState(false)\n  const [videoError, setVideoError] = useState(null)\n  const [playing, setPlaying] = useState(false)\n  const animRef = useRef(null)\n\n  // Poll detections\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const poll = setInterval(async () => {\n      try {\n        const data = await fetchAPI('/api/summary')\n        if (data.summary) {\n          setSummary(data.summary)\n          onSummaryUpdate?.(data.summary)\n        }\n        if (data.detections) setDetections(data.detections)\n      } catch {}\n    }, 500)\n    return () => clearInterval(poll)\n  }, [])\n\n  // Draw overlay\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const video = videoRef.current\n    const canvas = canvasRef.current\n    if (!video || !canvas) return\n    const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d')\n\n    const draw = () => {\n      if (!video || !ctx) return\n      const vw = video.offsetWidth || 640\n      const vh = video.offsetHeight || 360\n      if (canvas.width !== vw || canvas.height !== vh) {\n        canvas.width = vw; canvas.height = vh\n      }\n      ctx.clearRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height)\n      const sx = canvas.width / 1280\n      const sy = canvas.height / 720\n\n      detections.forEach(d => {\n        const [x1, y1, x2, y2] = d.bbox\n        const px1 = x1 * sx, py1 = y1 * sy, px2 = x2 * sx, py2 = y2 * sy\n        const pw = px2 - px1, ph = py2 - py1\n        const ok = d.ppe_status.compliant\n        const col = ok ? '#00c853' : '#ff1744'\n        ctx.strokeStyle = col; ctx.lineWidth = 2\n        ctx.strokeRect(px1, py1, pw, ph)\n        ctx.fillStyle = ok ? 'rgba(0,200,83,0.12)' : 'rgba(255,23,68,0.18)'\n        ctx.fillRect(px1, py1, pw, ph)\n        const label = ok ? 'OK' : `${!d.ppe_status.has_helmet ? 'NO-HELMET' : ''} ${!d.ppe_status.has_vest ? 'NO-VEST' : ''}`.trim()\n        ctx.font = 'bold 11px monospace'\n        const tw = ctx.measureText(label).width\n        ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)'\n        ctx.fillRect(px1, py1 - 18, tw + 8, 17)\n        ctx.fillStyle = col\n        ctx.fillText(label, px1 + 4, py1 - 5)\n      })\n\n      animRef.current = requestAnimationFrame(draw)\n    }\n    draw()\n    return () => { if (animRef.current) cancelAnimationFrame(animRef.current) }\n  }, [detections])\n\n  const col = summary?.compliance_rate >= 80 ? '#52c41a'\n    : summary?.compliance_rate >= 50 ? '#faad14' : '#ff4d4f'\n\n  return (\n    <div style={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 12 }}>\n\n      {/* ── TOP: Real Video + Boxes ── */}\n      <div style={{ position: 'relative', borderRadius: 12, overflow: 'hidden', background: '#000' }}>\n        <div style={{ position: 'relative', lineHeight: 0 }}>\n          <video\n            ref={videoRef}\n            src={VIDEO_URL}\n            controls autoPlay loop muted playsInline\n            style={{ width: '100%', display: 'block' }}\n            onCanPlay={() => setVideoReady(true)}\n            onError={() => setVideoError('Lỗi tải video')}\n            onPlay={() => setPlaying(true)}\n            onPause={() => setPlaying(false)}\n          />\n          <canvas\n            ref={canvasRef}\n            style={{ position: 'absolute', top: 0, left: 0, width: '100%', height: '100%', pointerEvents: 'none' }}\n          />\n        </div>\n\n        <div style={{\n          position: 'absolute', top: 10, right: 10,\n          background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)', borderRadius: 6, padding: '4px 10px',\n          fontSize: 10, color: '#0f0', fontFamily: 'monospace',\n        }}>\n          {playing ? '● LIVE' : '⏸ PAUSED'}\n        </div>\n        <div style={{\n          position: 'absolute', top: 10, left: 10,\n          background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.6)', borderRadius: 6, padding: '4px 10px',\n          fontSize: 10, color: '#aaa', fontFamily: 'monospace',\n        }}>\n          📹 VIDEO THỰC\n        </div>\n\n        {videoError && (\n          <div style={{\n            position: 'absolute', inset: 0, display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center',\n            justifyContent: 'center', background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.8)', color: '#ff4d4f',\n          }}>\n            {videoError}\n          </div>\n        )}\n        {!videoReady && !videoError && (\n          <div style={{\n            position: 'absolute', inset: 0, display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center',\n            justifyContent: 'center', background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)', color: '#aaa',\n            flexDirection: 'column', gap: 8,\n          }}>\n            <LoadingOutlined style={{ fontSize: 32 }} />\n            <span>Đang tải video...</span>\n          </div>\n        )}\n\n        {/* Stats overlay bottom */}\n        {summary && (\n          <div style={{\n            position: 'absolute', bottom: 10, left: 10,\n            background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.8)', borderRadius: 8, padding: '8px 12px',\n            fontFamily: 'monospace', fontSize: 11,\n          }}>\n            <div style={{ color: '#fff' }}>👤 {summary.total_persons || 0} phát hiện</div>\n            <div style={{ color: '#52c41a' }}>✅ {summary.compliant || 0} <span style={{ color: '#ff4d4f' }}>❌ {summary.violations || 0}</span></div>\n            <div style={{ color: col }}>📊 {summary.compliance_rate || 0}%</div>\n          </div>\n        )}\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ── BOTTOM: Annotated Frame ── */}\n      <div>\n        <div style={{ fontSize: 11, color: '#666', marginBottom: 6, fontFamily: 'monospace', paddingLeft: 4 }}>\n          📷 KẾT QUẢ NHẬN DIỆN (Frame từ Backend)\n        </div>\n        <AnnotatedFrame summary={summary} />\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  )\n}","newText":"// ── Plain Video (just for viewing) ───────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction VideoPlayer({ onSummaryUpdate }) {\n  const [videoReady, setVideoReady] = useState(false)\n  const [videoError, setVideoError] = useState(null)\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const poll = setInterval(async () => {\n      try {\n        const data = await fetchAPI('/api/summary')\n        if (data.summary) onSummaryUpdate?.(data.summary)\n      } catch {}\n    }, 1000)\n    return () => clearInterval(poll)\n  }, [])\n\n  return (\n    <div style={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 12 }}>\n\n      {/* ── TOP: Plain video (observation only) ── */}\n      <div style={{ position: 'relative', borderRadius: 12, overflow: 'hidden', background: '#000' }}>\n        <video\n          src={VIDEO_URL}\n          controls autoPlay loop muted playsInline\n          style={{ width: '100%', display: 'block' }}\n          onCanPlay={() => setVideoReady(true)}\n          onError={() => setVideoError('Không tải được video')}\n        />\n\n        <div style={{\n          position: 'absolute', top: 10, left: 10,\n          background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.6)', borderRadius: 6, padding: '4px 10px',\n          fontSize: 10, color: '#aaa', fontFamily: 'monospace',\n        }}>\n          📹 Quan sát thực tế\n        </div>\n\n        {videoError && (\n          <div style={{\n            position: 'absolute', inset: 0, display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center',\n            justifyContent: 'center', background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.8)', color: '#ff4d4f',\n          }}>\n            <div style={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>\n              <div style={{ marginBottom: 8 }}>⚠️ {videoError}</div>\n              <div style={{ fontSize: 12, color: '#888' }}>Kiểm tra đường dẫn: {VIDEO_URL}</div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        )}\n        {!videoReady && !videoError && (\n          <div style={{\n            position: 'absolute', inset: 0, display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center',\n            justifyContent: 'center', background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)', color: '#aaa',\n            flexDirection: 'column', gap: 8,\n          }}>\n            <LoadingOutlined style={{ fontSize: 32 }} />\n            <span>Đang tải video...</span>\n          </div>\n        )}\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ── BOTTOM: Annotated frame (surveillance) ── */}\n      <div>\n        <div style={{ fontSize: 11, color: '#666', marginBottom: 6, fontFamily: 'monospace', paddingLeft: 4 }}>\n          📷 GIÁM SÁT — Frame nhận diện PPE từ Backend\n        </div>\n        <AnnotatedFrame summary={null} />\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  )\n}"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":2807,"cacheRead":139449,"cacheWrite":372,"totalTokens":142628,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776791615103,"responseId":"0636e3405e37fba475e2f5340e93209a"}}
