{"type":"message","id":"f5c4daa7","parentId":"deb8bd08","timestamp":"2026-04-21T17:24:42.519Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The moov atom is at the END of the file. For streaming playback, the moov atom needs to be at the beginning of the file (before mdat). This is why the browser can't play the video - it needs to read the moov atom (which contains metadata like codec info, duration, etc.) before it can start decoding the mdat (media data).\n\nThis is a classic MP4 encoding issue. I need to re-encode the video with the moov atom positioned before mdat. I can use FFmpeg with `-movflags +faststart` to achieve this.\n\n\nLet me check if FFmpeg is installed and ready to use.","thinkingSignature":"438b650ce68763ef9634b4a738d735c9d3a9cffb31683bd56941bb6e9ce7eaf7"},{"type":"text","text":"Tìm ra vấn đề! File MP4 có `moov atom` ở **cuối** file — trình duyệt cần nó ở **đầu** để bắt đầu play. Fix bằng cách đặt moov trước mdat:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nruwq572myi1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which ffmpeg && ffmpeg -version 2>&1 | head -1","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":77,"output":261,"cacheRead":52838,"cacheWrite":288,"totalTokens":53464,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776792276294,"responseId":"0636e5d526673ee760b42a21505d1a3c"}}
