{"type":"message","id":"05777561","parentId":"60f2e69c","timestamp":"2026-04-21T17:25:33.589Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The apt-get was killed (probably disk space). Let me try another approach - use Python to manually rearrange the MP4 file to put moov at the beginning. I can also try using mp4box or handbrake-cli if available.\n\nActually, let me just use Python's struct module to parse and rearrange the MP4 atoms. This is doable without ffmpeg.","thinkingSignature":"890ba5f78055d8c4013b4d245a9e9d47a53c082e3f04f519066363a59c64cb7f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rjp5yh8g3s9h_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"import ffmpeg; print('ok')\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"no ffmpeg python\"\nwhich mp4box || which handbrake-cli || echo \"none available\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":59,"output":155,"cacheRead":53583,"cacheWrite":188,"totalTokens":53985,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776792328374,"responseId":"0636e609520ab44a3dd8420f69c71632"}}
