{"type":"message","id":"6485b6ed","parentId":"6bb8e7aa","timestamp":"2026-04-21T17:29:13.629Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to use an online/public video URL instead of the local file. Let me try to find a public video URL that will work. \n\nI need a public URL for a construction site video or similar. Let me try some approaches:\n\n1. Check if there are any publicly available construction safety videos\n2. Use a Pexels video URL (even though earlier we had issues with them)\n3. Use a sample video from a reliable CDN\n\nLet me try a few public video URLs. The key is they need to:\n- Be directly accessible (no referer check ideally)\n- Be H.264/MP4 format\n\n\n- Allow cross-origin access\n\nI'm thinking through some public video sources like Google's sample videos, Big Buck Bunny, and test videos from various CDNs. Since the user is Vietnamese, I'll try a few different public video URLs to see which one actually works with their setup.","thinkingSignature":"08e7ea496b40c13d9fb6497a8b15ebe3500483e02ff57d05a3ab72344968bf95"},{"type":"text","text":"\nĐược rồi! Thử dùng video public từ internet:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dcc0u79i6qpu_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"construction site safety workers video free download direct mp4 url","count":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":248,"cacheRead":60588,"cacheWrite":675,"totalTokens":61511,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776792545296,"responseId":"0636e6e2abaddccf4ba68a8a2571230f"}}
