{"type":"message","id":"cd80e6e2","parentId":"89ce63e9","timestamp":"2026-04-21T17:29:23.067Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me try using known public video URLs directly. I'll test a few:\n\n1. Big Buck Bunny (but this is cartoon)\n2. Sample videos from various CDNs\n3. Try to find a construction video from a public source\n\nLet me try a few known URLs:\n- https://commondatastorage.googleapis.com/gtv-videos-bucket/sample/ForBiggerBlazes.mp4\n- https://sample-videos.com/video321/mp4/720/big_buck_bunny_720p_1mb.mp4\n\nActually, for construction/PPE detection, any video showing people would work. Let me try the Big Buck Bunny or similar.\n\n\nI'm going to test some well-known public video URLs and see which ones actually load properly.","thinkingSignature":"9dfb69531084b5e7c66a2f1c05e0e2d1fd329477e07ed39464e076c5f48fae1d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u8c4fvgwgc2q_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test a few public video URLs for availability and CORS\nfor url in \\\n  \"https://commondatastorage.googleapis.com/gtv-videos-bucket/sample/BigBuckBunny.mp4\" \\\n  \"https://sample-videos.com/video321/mp4/720/big_buck_bunny_720p_1mb.mp4\" \\\n  \"https://www.w3schools.com/html/mov_bbb.mp4\" \\\n  \"https://test-videos.co.uk/vids/bigbuckbunny/mp4/h264/720/Big_Buck_Bunny_720_10s_1MB.mp4\"; do\n  code=$(curl -sI -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" --max-time 5 \"$url\")\n  echo \"$code  $url\"\ndone","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":131,"output":362,"cacheRead":60939,"cacheWrite":540,"totalTokens":61972,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776792555270,"responseId":"0636e6ecccfd1e4878897e7cd90add34"}}
