{"type":"message","id":"9b040855","parentId":"9fb5038a","timestamp":"2026-04-21T18:03:24.261Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-21 18:03 UTC] thực hiện tính năng là người dùng update video của người dùng vào để phân tích, hoặc là sử dụng camera"}],"timestamp":1776794604247}}
{"type":"message","id":"98af247f","parentId":"9b040855","timestamp":"2026-04-21T18:03:36.420Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to add the ability for users to:\n1. Upload their own video for analysis\n2. Use their webcam/camera for real-time analysis\n\nLet me implement these features in the React frontend. I'll add:\n1. An upload button that lets users select a video file\n2. A webcam/camera button that captures from the user's camera\n3. Update the VideoPlayer component to handle these sources\n\nFor the upload feature, I'll use a file input that reads the file and creates a blob URL.\nFor the camera feature, I'll use `navigator.mediaDevices.getUserMedia()` to get the webcam stream.\n\n\nNow I'm going to update the App.jsx component to integrate these new input options alongside the existing demo video functionality.","thinkingSignature":"798a7c1234e2b63d1ed4b223b39179cf97f24f223dcd1ef04fb1ecc031632235"},{"type":"text","text":"Được rồi! Thêm 2 tính năng: **Upload video** + **Camera/Webcam**:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yv0xn7zun6cu_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/frontend/src/App.jsx","limit":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":233,"cacheRead":80668,"cacheWrite":459,"totalTokens":81360,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776794604261,"responseId":"0636eeed5ee813bced3a0dada34d69a9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"64853531","parentId":"98af247f","timestamp":"2026-04-21T18:03:36.465Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yv0xn7zun6cu_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import { useState, useEffect, useRef } from 'react'\nimport { io } from 'socket.io-client'\nimport {\n  Layout, Card, Row, Col, Statistic, Tag, Badge,\n  Button, Space, Typography, Alert, Progress, List, Tooltip\n} from 'antd'\nimport {\n  SafetyOutlined, AlertOutlined, UserOutlined,\n  CheckCircleOutlined, StopOutlined,\n  VideoCameraOutlined, ReloadOutlined, CameraOutlined, LoadingOutlined\n} from '@ant-design/icons'\n\nconst { Header, Content, Sider } = Layout\nconst { Title, Text } = Typography\n\nconst API_BASE = import.meta.env.VITE_API_BASE || ''\n// Video: local file (construction site, H.264, browser-compatible)\nconst VIDEO_URL = '/video/demo.mp4'\n\nasync function fetchAPI(path) {\n  const res = await fetch(`${API_BASE}${path}`)\n  if (!res.ok) throw new Error(`${path} → ${res.status}`)\n  return res.json()\n}\n\n// ── Annotated Frame (surveillance) ───────────────────────────────────────\nfunction AnnotatedFrame({ summary: parentSummary }) {\n  const [imgSrc, setImgSrc] = useState(null)\n  const [summary, setSummary] = useState(parentSummary)\n  const [lastUpdate, setLastUpdate] = useState(null)\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const poll = setInterval(async () => {\n      try {\n        // Fetch frame image\n        const res = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/api/frame`, { cache: 'no-cache' })\n        if (res.ok) {\n          const blob = await res.blob()\n          setImgSrc(URL.createObjectURL(blob))\n          setLastUpdate(new Date().toLocaleTimeString())\n        }\n        // Fetch summary\n        const data = await fetchAPI('/api/summary')\n        if (data.summary) setSummary(data.summary)\n      } catch {}\n    }, 500)\n    return () => clearInterval(poll)\n  }, [])\n\n  const color = summary?.compliance_rate >= 80 ? '#52c41a'\n    : summary?.compliance_rate >= 50 ? '#faad14' : '#ff4d4f'\n\n  return (\n    <div style={{ position: 'relative', borderRadius: 12, overflow: 'hidden', background: '#000' }}>\n      {imgSrc ? (\n        <img src={imgSrc} alt=\"Giám sát\" style={{ width: '100%', display: 'block' }} />\n      ) : (\n        <div style={{\n          width: '100%', height: 320,\n          display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center',\n\n[333 more lines in file. Use offset=61 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776794616447}}
{"type":"message","id":"f65bfd9b","parentId":"64853531","timestamp":"2026-04-21T18:03:50.974Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to redesign the VideoPlayer to support three modes:1. Demo video (local file)\n2. Uploaded video (user selects a file)\n3. Webcam (live camera feed)\n\nFor webcam, I'll need to:\n- Use navigator.mediaDevices.getUserMedia() to get the camera stream\n- Display the stream in a video element\n- The detection system currently processes frames from the backend's video processor (which reads from a video file). For webcam, we need to send frames to the backend for processing.\n\nActually, the current architecture has the backend doing the detection on frames from a video file. For webcam, we'd need to:\n- Capture frames from the canvas/video element\n\n\n- Send them to the backend via an API endpoint that accepts frame data, then process and return the annotated frames along with detection results. I could either stream frames directly to the backend as blob URLs or base64 images, or use WebRTC for peer-to-peer video transmission. The most straightforward approach would be to leverage the existing Flask/Socket.IO infrastructure and add an endpoint for sending individual frames from the browser.\n\nSince the backend is already processing frames from the demo video, I need to add a new API endpoint that accepts frame data and detection results, then update the frontend to send webcam frames to this endpoint and display the processed results.\n\nFor simplicity, I'll support both uploaded videos and webcam streams by adding a frame upload endpoint to Flask, sending frames from the browser via periodic POST requests, and storing the latest detection results in memory for the summary API to return.\n\nActually, I'm realizing this approach adds significant complexity. Let me think about a simpler solution: I can start with just video upload functionality, where the user selects a file, we upload it to the backend, and then process it the same way we're already handling the demo video.\n\nFor the webcam, I could render the live feed directly on the frontend using the browser's getUserMedia API, then periodically capture frames and send them to a new detection endpoint on the backend that processes images and returns annotations. The key challenge is getting those detection results back to display on top of the video, which might require using a canvas overlay approach rather than trying to embed the annotated results from the backend.\n\nI think the cleanest solution is to build this with three distinct modes: a demo video player that shows the existing annotated frames from the backend, a file upload mode that sends videos to the backend for processing, and a live webcam mode where the frontend sends frames to the backend API and renders the bounding boxes locally on a canvas overlay. I'll need to create an endpoint that accepts image uploads and returns detection results, then build the webcam mode to send frames there and draw the results directly on the canvas.","thinkingSignature":"ca0c0000cadb9fd38a7d40efaf6149851171768bfa98ec2e13e6469fbe05c02b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d3g82orzbavj_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/frontend/src/App.jsx","offset":61,"limit":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":357,"output":615,"cacheRead":81602,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82574,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776794616473,"responseId":"0636eefa0b844acd2a2bcc143103c0a0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a5ca1f2","parentId":"f65bfd9b","timestamp":"2026-04-21T18:03:51.026Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_d3g82orzbavj_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"          background: '#1a1a2e', color: '#555', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 12,\n        }}>\n          <VideoCameraOutlined style={{ fontSize: 40 }} />\n          <span>Đang kết nối camera giám sát...</span>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      <div style={{\n        position: 'absolute', top: 10, left: 10,\n        background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)', borderRadius: 6, padding: '4px 10px',\n        fontSize: 10, color: '#aaa', fontFamily: 'monospace',\n      }}>\n        Cập nhật: {lastUpdate || '...'}\n      </div>\n\n      <div style={{\n        position: 'absolute', top: 10, right: 10,\n        background: summary && !summary.compliant && summary.violations > 0 ? 'rgba(255,23,68,0.8)' : 'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)',\n        borderRadius: 6, padding: '4px 10px',\n        fontSize: 10, color: '#0f0', fontFamily: 'monospace',\n      }}>\n        {summary && !summary.compliant && summary.violations > 0 ? '⚠ ALERT' : '● LIVE'}\n      </div>\n\n      {summary && (\n        <div style={{\n          position: 'absolute', bottom: 10, left: 10,\n          background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.85)', borderRadius: 8, padding: '10px 14px',\n          fontFamily: 'monospace', fontSize: 12,\n        }}>\n          <div style={{ color: '#fff', marginBottom: 4 }}>👤 {summary.total_persons || 0} phát hiện</div>\n          <div style={{ color: '#52c41a' }}>✅ {summary.compliant || 0}</div>\n          <div style={{ color: '#ff4d4f' }}>❌ {summary.violations || 0}</div>\n          <div style={{ color, marginTop: 4, fontSize: 14, fontWeight: 700 }}>\n            📊 {summary.compliance_rate || 0}%\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n\n// ── Plain Video (just for viewing) ───────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction VideoPlayer({ onSummaryUpdate }) {\n  const [videoReady, setVideoReady] = useState(false)\n  const [videoError, setVideoError] = useState(null)\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const poll = setInterval(async () => {\n      try {\n        const data = await fetchAPI('/api/summary')\n        if (data.summary) onSummaryUpdate?.(data.summary)\n      } catch {}\n    }, 1000)\n    return () => clearInterval(poll)\n  }, [])\n\n  return (\n    <div style={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 12 }}>\n\n      {/* ── TOP: Plain video (observation only) ── */}\n      <div style={{ position: 'relative', borderRadius: 12, overflow: 'hidden', background: '#000' }}>\n        <video\n          src={VIDEO_URL}\n          controls autoPlay loop muted playsInline\n          style={{ width: '100%', display: 'block' }}\n          onCanPlay={() => setVideoReady(true)}\n          onError={() => setVideoError('Không tải được video')}\n        />\n\n        <div style={{\n          position: 'absolute', top: 10, left: 10,\n          background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.6)', borderRadius: 6, padding: '4px 10px',\n          fontSize: 10, color: '#aaa', fontFamily: 'monospace',\n        }}>\n          📹 Quan sát thực tế\n        </div>\n\n        {videoError && (\n          <div style={{\n            position: 'absolute', inset: 0, display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center',\n            justifyContent: 'center', background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.8)', color: '#ff4d4f',\n          }}>\n            <div style={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>\n              <div style={{ marginBottom: 8 }}>⚠️ {videoError}</div>\n              <div style={{ fontSize: 12, color: '#888' }}>Kiểm tra đường dẫn: {VIDEO_URL}</div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        )}\n        {!videoReady && !videoError && (\n          <div style={{\n            position: 'absolute', inset: 0, display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center',\n            justifyContent: 'center', background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)', color: '#aaa',\n            flexDirection: 'column', gap: 8,\n          }}>\n            <LoadingOutlined style={{ fontSize: 32 }} />\n            <span>Đang tải video...</span>\n          </div>\n        )}\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ── BOTTOM: Annotated frame (surveillance) ── */}\n      <div>\n        <div style={{ fontSize: 11, color: '#666', marginBottom: 6, fontFamily: 'monospace', paddingLeft: 4 }}>\n          📷 GIÁM SÁT — Frame nhận diện PPE từ Backend\n        </div>\n        <AnnotatedFrame summary={null} />\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n\n// ── Alert Item ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction AlertItem({ alert }) {\n  const d = alert.detection || {}\n  const ok = d.compliant\n  return (\n    <List.Item style={{ padding: '8px 0' }}>\n      <Space align=\"start\" style={{ width: '100%' }}>\n\n[213 more lines in file. Use offset=181 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776794631011}}
{"type":"message","id":"e9fa2a2b","parentId":"2a5ca1f2","timestamp":"2026-04-21T18:05:11.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to redesign the VideoPlayer to support 3 modes:1. Demo video (default, local file)\n2. Upload mode (user uploads a video file → backend processes it)\n3. Camera mode (live webcam)For modes 2 and 3, I need the backend to handle uploaded video files. Let me first update the backend to support video upload, then update the frontend.For the backend, I'll add:- `POST /api/upload-video` - upload a video file and start processing it- The video processor will read from the uploaded fileFor the frontend:- File input for upload\n- getUserMedia for webcam\n- The VideoPlayer will have a mode selector\n\n\nNow I'm implementing this with a mode selector at the top, demo video by default, an upload button that sends files to the backend, and a webcam button that uses getUserMedia for live streaming. The webcam mode will capture frames and send them to a new detection endpoint that processes them and returns results, which I'll then draw on a canvas overlay in real-time.","thinkingSignature":"2b56646401f1e01238c5132f6a9df01f0f7ce0f440d9ddca9a38413a1c816262"},{"type":"text","text":"Viết lại hoàn toàn VideoPlayer với 3 chế độ + backend hỗ trợ upload:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gus4jxadvnbi_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/frontend/src/App.jsx","content":"import { useState, useEffect, useRef } from 'react'\nimport { io } from 'socket.io-client'\nimport {\n  Layout, Card, Row, Col, Statistic, Tag, Badge,\n  Button, Space, Typography, Alert, Progress, List, Tooltip, Upload, message, Modal\n} from 'antd'\nimport {\n  SafetyOutlined, AlertOutlined, UserOutlined,\n  CheckCircleOutlined, StopOutlined,\n  VideoCameraOutlined, ReloadOutlined, CameraOutlined,\n  LoadingOutlined, UploadOutlined, CloudUploadOutlined\n} from '@ant-design/icons'\n\nconst { Header, Content, Sider } = Layout\nconst { Title, Text } = Typography\n\nconst API_BASE = import.meta.env.VITE_API_BASE || ''\n\nasync function fetchAPI(path, opts = {}) {\n  const res = await fetch(`${API_BASE}${path}`, opts)\n  if (!res.ok) throw new Error(`${path} → ${res.status}`)\n  return res.json()\n}\n\n// ── Source Selector ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n// 'demo' | 'upload' | 'camera'\nfunction SourceSelector({ source, onSourceChange, onUpload }) {\n  const fileRef = useRef(null)\n\n  const handleUpload = async (file) => {\n    message.loading({ content: 'Đang tải video lên...', key: 'upload' })\n    try {\n      const formData = new FormData()\n      formData.append('video', file)\n      const res = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/api/upload-video`, {\n        method: 'POST',\n        body: formData,\n      })\n      if (!res.ok) throw new Error('Upload failed')\n      const data = await res.json()\n      message.success({ content: `Video \"${file.name}\" đã sẵn sàng!`, key: 'upload' })\n      onUpload(data.video_path || URL.createObjectURL(file))\n    } catch (e) {\n      message.error({ content: `Lỗi: ${e.message}`, key: 'upload' })\n    }\n    return false // prevent default upload\n  }\n\n  return (\n    <div style={{\n      display: 'flex', gap: 8, marginBottom: 12,\n      flexWrap: 'wrap', alignItems: 'center',\n    }}>\n      <Text style={{ color: '#888', fontSize: 12, marginRight: 4 }}>Nguồn:</Text>\n\n      <Tag\n        icon={<VideoCameraOutlined />}\n        color={source === 'demo' ? 'blue' : 'default'}\n        onClick={() => onSourceChange('demo')}\n        style={{ cursor: 'pointer', padding: '4px 12px', fontSize: 12 }}\n      >\n        Video Demo\n      </Tag>\n\n      <Upload\n        beforeUpload={handleUpload}\n        showUploadList={false}\n        accept=\"video/*\"\n      >\n        <Tag\n          icon={<UploadOutlined />}\n          color={source === 'upload' ? 'green' : 'default'}\n          onClick={() => onSourceChange('upload')}\n          style={{ cursor: 'pointer', padding: '4px 12px', fontSize: 12 }}\n        >\n          Tải Video Lên\n        </Tag>\n      </Upload>\n\n      <Tag\n        icon={<CameraOutlined />}\n        color={source === 'camera' ? 'orange' : 'default'}\n        onClick={() => onSourceChange('camera')}\n        style={{ cursor: 'pointer', padding: '4px 12px', fontSize: 12 }}\n      >\n        Camera/Webcam\n      </Tag>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n\n// ── Camera Mode ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction CameraMode({ onSummaryUpdate }) {\n  const videoRef = useRef(null)\n  const canvasRef = useRef(null)\n  const streamRef = useRef(null)\n  const animRef = useRef(null)\n  const [cameraOn, setCameraOn] = useState(false)\n  const [cameraError, setCameraError] = useState(null)\n  const [detections, setDetections] = useState([])\n  const [summary, setSummary] = useState(null)\n\n  const stopCamera = () => {\n    if (streamRef.current) {\n      streamRef.current.getTracks().forEach(t => t.stop())\n      streamRef.current = null\n    }\n    if (animRef.current) cancelAnimationFrame(animRef.current)\n    setCameraOn(false)\n  }\n\n  const startCamera = async () => {\n    try {\n      const stream = await navigator.mediaDevices.getUserMedia({\n        video: { width: { ideal: 1280 }, height: { ideal: 720 }, facingMode: 'environment' },\n        audio: false,\n      })\n      streamRef.current = stream\n      if (videoRef.current) {\n        videoRef.current.srcObject = stream\n        videoRef.current.play()\n      }\n      setCameraOn(true)\n      setCameraError(null)\n    } catch (e) {\n      setCameraError(e.message || 'Không truy cập được camera')\n    }\n  }\n\n  // Process frames from camera\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (!cameraOn) return\n    const video = videoRef.current\n    const canvas = canvasRef.current\n    if (!video || !canvas) return\n    const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d')\n\n    const processFrame = async () => {\n      if (video.readyState >= 2) {\n        // Draw video frame to canvas\n        if (canvas.width !== video.videoWidth) canvas.width = video.videoWidth || 640\n        if (canvas.height !== video.videoHeight) canvas.height = video.videoHeight || 480\n        ctx.drawImage(video, 0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height)\n\n        // Send frame to backend\n        try {\n          const blob = await new Promise(resolve => canvas.toBlob(resolve, 'image/jpeg', 0.7))\n          const formData = new FormData()\n          formData.append('frame', blob, 'frame.jpg')\n\n          const res = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/api/detect-frame`, {\n            method: 'POST',\n            body: formData,\n            timeout: 5000,\n          })\n          if (res.ok) {\n            const data = await res.json()\n            if (data.detections) setDetections(data.detections)\n            if (data.summary) {\n              setSummary(data.summary)\n              onSummaryUpdate?.(data.summary)\n            }\n          }\n        } catch {}\n\n        // Draw detections on canvas overlay\n        ctx.clearRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height)\n        const scaleX = canvas.width / (data?.frame_width || canvas.width)\n        const scaleY = canvas.height / (data?.frame_height || canvas.height)\n\n        detections.forEach(d => {\n          const [x1, y1, x2, y2] = d.bbox\n          const px1 = x1 * scaleX, py1 = y1 * scaleY\n          const px2 = x2 * scaleX, py2 = y2 * scaleY\n          const ok = d.ppe_status?.compliant\n          const col = ok ? '#00c853' : '#ff1744'\n          ctx.strokeStyle = col; ctx.lineWidth = 2\n          ctx.strokeRect(px1, py1, px2 - px1, py2 - py1)\n          ctx.fillStyle = ok ? 'rgba(0,200,83,0.15)' : 'rgba(255,23,68,0.2)'\n          ctx.fillRect(px1, py1, px2 - px1, py2 - py1)\n          const label = ok ? 'OK' : [\n            !d.ppe_status?.has_helmet && 'NO-HELMET',\n            !d.ppe_status?.has_vest && 'NO-VEST',\n          ].filter(Boolean).join('+') || 'VIOLATION'\n          ctx.font = 'bold 13px monospace'\n          const tw = ctx.measureText(label).width\n          ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)'\n          ctx.fillRect(px1, py1 - 20, tw + 10, 19)\n          ctx.fillStyle = col\n          ctx.fillText(label, px1 + 5, py1 - 6)\n        })\n      }\n      animRef.current = requestAnimationFrame(processFrame)\n    }\n\n    processFrame()\n    return () => {\n      if (animRef.current) cancelAnimationFrame(animRef.current)\n      stopCamera()\n    }\n  }, [cameraOn])\n\n  const color = summary?.compliance_rate >= 80 ? '#52c41a'\n    : summary?.compliance_rate >= 50 ? '#faad14' : '#ff4d4f'\n\n  return (\n    <div>\n      {!cameraOn ? (\n        <div style={{\n          width: '100%', height: 320,\n          display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column',\n          alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center',\n          background: '#1a1a2e', color: '#555',\n          borderRadius: 12, gap: 16,\n        }}>\n          <CameraOutlined style={{ fontSize: 48 }} />\n          {cameraError ? (\n            <div style={{ color: '#ff4d4f', textAlign: 'center', padding: '0 20px', fontSize: 13 }}>\n              <div>⚠️ Lỗi camera</div>\n              <div style={{ color: '#888', fontSize: 12, marginTop: 4 }}>{cameraError}</div>\n              <Button type=\"primary\" size=\"small\" style={{ marginTop: 12 }} onClick={startCamera}>\n                Thử lại\n              </Button>\n            </div>\n          ) : (\n            <>\n              <span>Camera chưa bật</span>\n              <Button type=\"primary\" icon={<CameraOutlined />} onClick={startCamera}>\n                Bật Camera\n              </Button>\n            </>\n          )}\n        </div>\n      ) : (\n        <div style={{ position: 'relative', borderRadius: 12, overflow: 'hidden', background: '#000' }}>\n          <video\n            ref={videoRef}\n            autoPlay playsInline muted\n            style={{ width: '100%', display: 'block', background: '#000' }}\n          />\n          <canvas\n            ref={canvasRef}\n            style={{\n              position: 'absolute', top: 0, left: 0,\n              width: '100%', height: '100%', pointerEvents: 'none',\n            }}\n          />\n\n          <div style={{\n            position: 'absolute', top: 10, left: 10,\n            background: 'rgba(255,23,68,0.8)', borderRadius: 6, padding: '4px 10px',\n            fontSize: 10, color: '#fff', fontFamily: 'monospace',\n          }}>\n            ● LIVE CAMERA\n          </div>\n\n          <div style={{\n            position: 'absolute', top: 10, right: 10,\n            background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)', borderRadius: 6, padding: '4px 10px',\n          }}>\n            <Button\n              size=\"small\" danger\n              onClick={stopCamera}\n              style={{ fontSize: 11, padding: '0 8px', height: 24 }}\n            >\n              Tắt Camera\n            </Button>\n          </div>\n\n          {summary && (\n            <div style={{\n              position: 'absolute', bottom: 10, left: 10,\n              background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.85)', borderRadius: 8,\n              padding: '8px 12px', fontFamily: 'monospace', fontSize: 11,\n            }}>\n              <div style={{ color: '#fff' }}>👤 {summary.total_persons || 0} phát hiện</div>\n              <div style={{ color: '#52c41a' }}>✅ {summary.compliant || 0} <span style={{ color: '#ff4d4f' }}>❌ {summary.violations || 0}</span></div>\n              <div style={{ color, fontWeight: 700 }}>📊 {summary.compliance_rate || 0}%</div>\n            </div>\n          )}\n        </div>\n      )}\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n\n// ── Video Player (all modes) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction VideoPlayer({ onSummaryUpdate }) {\n  const [source, setSource] = useState('demo')\n  const [uploadedUrl, setUploadedUrl] = useState(null)\n  const [videoReady, setVideoReady] = useState(false)\n  const [videoError, setVideoError] = useState(null)\n\n  const demoUrl = '/video/demo.mp4'\n\n  const currentSrc = source === 'upload' && uploadedUrl\n    ? uploadedUrl\n    : demoUrl\n\n  return (\n    <div style={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 12 }}>\n\n      {/* Source selector */}\n      <SourceSelector\n        source={source}\n        onSourceChange={(s) => {\n          setSource(s)\n          setVideoReady(false)\n          setVideoError(null)\n        }}\n        onUpload={(url) => {\n          setUploadedUrl(url)\n          setSource('upload')\n        }}\n      />\n\n      {/* ── TOP: Video view (demo or upload or camera) ── */}\n      <div style={{ position: 'relative', borderRadius: 12, overflow: 'hidden', background: '#000' }}>\n        {source === 'camera' ? (\n          <CameraMode onSummaryUpdate={onSummaryUpdate} />\n        ) : (\n          <>\n            <video\n              src={currentSrc}\n              controls autoPlay loop muted playsInline\n              style={{ width: '100%', display: 'block', background: '#000' }}\n              onCanPlay={() => setVideoReady(true)}\n              onError={() => setVideoError('Không tải được video')}\n            />\n\n            <div style={{\n              position: 'absolute', top: 10, left: 10,\n              background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.6)', borderRadius: 6, padding: '4px 10px',\n              fontSize: 10, color: '#aaa', fontFamily: 'monospace',\n            }}>\n              📹 {source === 'upload' ? 'Video tải lên' : 'Video Demo'}\n            </div>\n\n            {videoError && (\n              <div style={{\n                position: 'absolute', inset: 0, display: 'flex',\n                alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center',\n                background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.8)', color: '#ff4d4f',\n              }}>\n                <div style={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>\n                  <div>⚠️ {videoError}</div>\n                  <div style={{ fontSize: 12, color: '#888', marginTop: 4 }}>\n                    Thử tải video khác hoặc dùng Camera\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            )}\n            {!videoReady && !videoError && (\n              <div style={{\n                position: 'absolute', inset: 0, display: 'flex',\n                alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center',\n                background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)', color: '#aaa',\n                flexDirection: 'column', gap: 8,\n              }}>\n                <LoadingOutlined style={{ fontSize: 32 }} />\n                <span>Đang tải video...</span>\n              </div>\n            )}\n          </>\n        )}\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ── BOTTOM: Annotated frame from backend ── */}\n      <div>\n        <div style={{ fontSize: 11, color: '#666', marginBottom: 6, fontFamily: 'monospace', paddingLeft: 4 }}>\n          📷 KẾT QUẢ NHẬN DIỆN PPE — {source === 'camera' ? 'Xử lý real-time' : 'Frame từ Backend'}\n        </div>\n        <AnnotatedFrame source={source} onSummaryUpdate={onSummaryUpdate} />\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n\n// ── Annotated Frame ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction AnnotatedFrame({ source, onSummaryUpdate }) {\n  const [imgSrc, setImgSrc] = useState(null)\n  const [summary, setSummary] = useState(null)\n  const [lastUpdate, setLastUpdate] = useState(null)\n  const [connected, setConnected] = useState(false)\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    // Poll for annotated frame from backend\n    const poll = setInterval(async () => {\n      try {\n        const res = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/api/frame`, { cache: 'no-cache' })\n        if (res.ok) {\n          const blob = await res.blob()\n          setImgSrc(URL.createObjectURL(blob))\n          setLastUpdate(new Date().toLocaleTimeString())\n          setConnected(true)\n        }\n        const data = await fetchAPI('/api/summary')\n        if (data.summary) {\n          setSummary(data.summary)\n          onSummaryUpdate?.(data.summary)\n        }\n      } catch {\n        setConnected(false)\n      }\n    }, source === 'camera' ? 800 : 500)\n    return () => clearInterval(poll)\n  }, [source])\n\n  const color = summary?.compliance_rate >= 80 ? '#52c41a'\n    : summary?.compliance_rate >= 50 ? '#faad14' : '#ff4d4f'\n\n  return (\n    <div style={{ position: 'relative', borderRadius: 12, overflow: 'hidden', background: '#000' }}>\n      {imgSrc ? (\n        <img src={imgSrc} alt=\"Giám sát\" style={{ width: '100%', display: 'block' }} />\n      ) : (\n        <div style={{\n          width: '100%', height: 300,\n          display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center',\n          background: '#1a1a2e', color: '#555', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 12,\n        }}>\n          <VideoCameraOutlined style={{ fontSize: 40 }} />\n          <span>Đang kết nối camera giám sát...</span>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      <div style={{\n        position: 'absolute', top: 10, left: 10,\n        background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)', borderRadius: 6, padding: '4px 10px',\n        fontSize: 10, color: '#aaa', fontFamily: 'monospace',\n      }}>\n        Cập nhật: {lastUpdate || '...'}\n      </div>\n\n      <div style={{\n        position: 'absolute', top: 10, right: 10,\n        background: connected\n          ? (summary && !summary.compliant && summary.violations > 0 ? 'rgba(255,23,68,0.8)' : 'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)')\n          : 'rgba(255,140,0,0.8)',\n        borderRadius: 6, padding: '4px 10px',\n        fontSize: 10, color: '#fff', fontFamily: 'monospace',\n      }}>\n        {connected\n          ? (summary && !summary.compliant && summary.violations > 0 ? '⚠ ALERT' : '● LIVE')\n          : '○ CONNECTING'}\n      </div>\n\n      {summary && (\n        <div style={{\n          position: 'absolute', bottom: 10, left: 10,\n          background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.85)', borderRadius: 8,\n          padding: '10px 14px', fontFamily: 'monospace', fontSize: 12,\n        }}>\n          <div style={{ color: '#fff', marginBottom: 4 }}>👤 {summary.total_persons || 0} phát hiện</div>\n          <div style={{ color: '#52c41a' }}>✅ {summary.compliant || 0} <span style={{ color: '#ff4d4f' }}>❌ {summary.violations || 0}</span></div>\n          <div style={{ color, marginTop: 4, fontSize: 14, fontWeight: 700 }}>📊 {summary.compliance_rate || 0}%</div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n\n// ── Alert Item ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction AlertItem({ alert }) {\n  const d = alert.detection || {}\n  const ok = d.compliant\n  return (\n    <List.Item style={{ padding: '8px 0' }}>\n      <Space align=\"start\" style={{ width: '100%' }}>\n        <Badge status={ok ? 'success' : 'error'} />\n        <div style={{ flex: 1 }}>\n          <Space>\n            {d.has_helmet === false && <Tag color=\"red\">NO HELMET</Tag>}\n            {d.has_vest === false && <Tag color=\"orange\">NO VEST</Tag>}\n            {ok && <Tag color=\"green\">OK</Tag>}\n          </Space>\n          <div style={{ fontSize: 11, color: '#999', marginTop: 2 }}>\n            {alert.timestamp ? new Date(alert.timestamp).toLocaleTimeString() : '—'}\n            {' · conf: '}{d.confidence?.toFixed(2) || '—'}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </Space>\n    </List.Item>\n  )\n}\n\n// ── Stats Card ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction StatsCard({ title, value, icon, color, sub }) {\n  return (\n    <Card size=\"small\" style={{ borderRadius: 12 }}>\n      <Statistic\n        title={<Text type=\"secondary\" style={{ fontSize: 13 }}>{title}</Text>}\n        value={value}\n        valueStyle={{ color, fontSize: 28, fontWeight: 700 }}\n        prefix={<span style={{ marginRight: 8 }}>{icon}</span>}\n      />\n      {sub && <div style={{ marginTop: 4, fontSize: 12, color: '#888' }}>{sub}</div>}\n    </Card>\n  )\n}\n\n// ── Main App ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nexport default function App() {\n  const [summary, setSummary] = useState({\n    total_persons: 0, compliant: 0, violations: 0,\n    no_helmet: 0, no_vest: 0, compliance_rate: 100,\n  })\n  const [alerts, setAlerts] = useState([])\n  const [status, setStatus] = useState('connecting')\n  const [alertStats, setAlertStats] = useState({})\n\n  // Socket.IO\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const socket = io(API_BASE || window.location.origin, {\n      transports: ['websocket', 'polling'],\n      reconnectionAttempts: 5, reconnectionDelay: 2000,\n    })\n    socket.on('connect', () => {\n      socket.emit('subscribe', { camera_id: 'demo-camera' })\n      setStatus('live')\n    })\n    socket.on('disconnect', () => setStatus('stopped'))\n    socket.on('detection_summary', (data) => {\n      if (data.summary) setSummary(data.summary)\n    })\n    socket.on('ppe_alert', (alert) => {\n      setAlerts(prev => [alert, ...prev].slice(0, 100))\n      try {\n        const audio = new Audio(\n          'data:audio/wav;base64,'\n        )\n        audio.volume = 0.3\n        audio.play().catch(() => {})\n      } catch {}\n    })\n    return () => socket.disconnect()\n  }, [])\n\n  // Poll alerts\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const load = async () => {\n      try {\n        const [ad, sd] = await Promise.all([\n          fetchAPI('/api/alerts?limit=20'),\n          fetchAPI('/api/alerts/stats').catch(() => ({})),\n        ])\n        if (Array.isArray(ad)) setAlerts(ad)\n        if (sd && !sd.error) setAlertStats(sd)\n      } catch {}\n    }\n    load()\n    const iv = setInterval(load, 10000)\n    return () => clearInterval(iv)\n  }, [])\n\n  const col = summary.compliance_rate >= 80 ? '#52c41a'\n    : summary.compliance_rate >= 50 ? '#faad14' : '#ff4d4f'\n\n  return (\n    <Layout style={{ minHeight: '100vh', background: '#0f0f1a' }}>\n      <Header style={{\n        background: '#1a1a2e', borderBottom: '1px solid #2a2a4a',\n        display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'space-between',\n        padding: '0 24px',\n      }}>\n        <Space>\n          <SafetyOutlined style={{ fontSize: 24, color: '#faad14' }} />\n          <Title level={4} style={{ color: '#fff', margin: 0 }}>PPE Safety Monitor</Title>\n          <Badge\n            status={status === 'live' ? 'processing' : 'error'}\n            text={<Text style={{ color: status === 'live' ? '#52c41a' : '#ff4d4f', fontSize: 12 }}>\n              {status === 'live' ? 'LIVE' : 'CONNECTING'}\n            </Text>}\n          />\n        </Space>\n        <Space>\n          <Tooltip title=\"Reload\">\n            <Button icon={<ReloadOutlined />} onClick={() => fetchAPI('/api/alerts?limit=20').then(d => Array.isArray(d) && setAlerts(d))}>\n              Reload\n            </Button>\n          </Tooltip>\n          <Tag style={{ background: '#16213e', border: 'none', color: '#aaa' }}>\n            S1 Safety System v1.0\n          </Tag>\n        </Space>\n      </Header>\n\n      <Layout>\n        <Content style={{ padding: 20, background: '#0f0f1a' }}>\n          {/* Stats */}\n          <Row gutter={[16, 16]} style={{ marginBottom: 20 }}>\n            <Col xs={24} sm={12} md={6}>\n              <StatsCard title=\"Tổng người\" value={summary.total_persons} icon={<UserOutlined />} color=\"#1890ff\" />\n            </Col>\n            <Col xs={24} sm={12} md={6}>\n              <StatsCard title=\"Tuân thủ ✓\" value={summary.compliant} icon={<CheckCircleOutlined />} color=\"#52c41a\" />\n            </Col>\n            <Col xs={24} sm={12} md={6}>\n              <StatsCard title=\"Vi phạm ✗\" value={summary.violations} icon={<StopOutlined />} color=\"#ff4d4f\"\n                sub={summary.no_helmet > 0 ? `• Không mũ: ${summary.no_helmet}` : null}\n              />\n            </Col>\n            <Col xs={24} sm={12} md={6}>\n              <Card size=\"small\" style={{ borderRadius: 12 }}>\n                <Statistic\n                  title={<Text type=\"secondary\" style={{ fontSize: 13 }}>Tỷ lệ tuân thủ</Text>}\n                  value={summary.compliance_rate} suffix=\"%\"\n                  valueStyle={{ color: col, fontSize: 28, fontWeight: 700 }}\n                  prefix={<SafetyOutlined style={{ marginRight: 8 }} />}\n                />\n                <Progress percent={summary.compliance_rate} showInfo={false} strokeColor={col} style={{ marginTop: 8 }} />\n              </Card>\n            </Col>\n          </Row>\n\n          {/* Video + Alert */}\n          <Row gutter={[16, 16]}>\n            <Col xs={24} lg={14}>\n              <Card\n                title={<Space><VideoCameraOutlined />Camera Feed</Space>}\n                style={{ background: '#1a1a2e', border: '1px solid #2a2a4a' }}\n                styles={{ header: { color: '#fff', borderBottom: '1px solid #2a2a4a' } }}\n              >\n                <VideoPlayer onSummaryUpdate={setSummary} />\n                <Alert\n                  message=\"Chọn nguồn: Video Demo | Tải Video Lên | Camera/Webcam\"\n                  type=\"info\" showIcon style={{ marginTop: 12 }}\n                />\n              </Card>\n            </Col>\n\n            <Col xs={24} lg={10}>\n              <Card\n                title={<Space><AlertOutlined style={{ color: '#ff4d4f' }} />Cảnh báo<Badge count={alerts.length} style={{ backgroundColor: '#ff4d4f' }} /></Space>}\n                style={{ background: '#1a1a2e', border: '1px solid #2a2a4a', height: '100%' }}\n                styles={{ header: { color: '#fff', borderBottom: '1px solid #2a2a4a' } }}\n                bodyStyle={{ maxHeight: 500, overflow: 'auto' }}\n              >\n                {alerts.length === 0 ? (\n                  <div style={{ textAlign: 'center', padding: 40, color: '#555' }}>\n                    <SafetyOutlined style={{ fontSize: 48, marginBottom: 12 }} />\n                    <div>Không có cảnh báo</div>\n                    <div style={{ fontSize: 12, marginTop: 4 }}>Hệ thống hoạt động bình thường</div>\n                  </div>\n                ) : (\n                  <List dataSource={alerts} renderItem={item => <AlertItem alert={item} />} locale={{ emptyText: 'Không có cảnh báo' }} />\n                )}\n              </Card>\n            </Col>\n          </Row>\n        </Content>\n\n        {/* Sidebar */}\n        <Sider width={240} style={{ background: '#1a1a2e', borderLeft: '1px solid #2a2a4a', padding: 16 }}>\n          <Title level={5} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>Thống kê 24h</Title>\n          <Space direction=\"vertical\" style={{ width: '100%' }} size={12}>\n            <Card size=\"small\" style={{ background: '#16213e' }}>\n              <Statistic title={<Text style={{ color: '#aaa', fontSize: 12 }}>Tổng cảnh báo</Text>}\n                value={alertStats.total || alerts.length} valueStyle={{ color: '#fff', fontSize: 24 }} />\n            </Card>\n            <Card size=\"small\" style={{ background: '#16213e' }}>\n              <Statistic title={<Text style={{ color: '#aaa', fontSize: 12 }}>Không đội mũ</Text>}\n                value={alertStats.no_helmet || 0} valueStyle={{ color: '#ff4d4f', fontSize: 24 }} />\n            </Card>\n            <Card size=\"small\" style={{ background: '#16213e' }}>\n              <Statistic title={<Text style={{ color: '#aaa', fontSize: 12 }}>Không áo phản quang</Text>}\n                value={alertStats.no_vest || 0} valueStyle={{ color: '#faad14', fontSize: 24 }} />\n            </Card>\n            <div style={{ marginTop: 16 }}>\n              <Title level={5} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>Hướng dẫn</Title>\n              <Card size=\"small\" style={{ background: '#16213e', fontSize: 12 }}>\n                <div style={{ color: '#aaa', lineHeight: 1.8, fontSize: 12 }}>\n                  <div>📹 <b>Demo:</b> Video có sẵn</div>\n                  <div>⬆ <b>Upload:</b> Tải video của bạn</div>\n                  <div>📷 <b>Camera:</b> Webcam realtime</div>\n                </div>\n              </Card>\n            </div>\n          </Space>\n        </Sider>\n      </Layout>\n    </Layout>\n  )\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1358,"output":7638,"cacheRead":81090,"cacheWrite":1452,"totalTokens":91538,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776794631033,"responseId":"0636ef08356903fe57990d54084fee54"}}
