{"type":"message","id":"68930984","parentId":"6d309094","timestamp":"2026-04-21T18:18:05.815Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so after 40 warm-up frames, we get 2 people per frame consistently. That's actually reasonable for the demo. The issue is that not all 4 workers are being detected because:\n1. The workers in the synthetic video are fairly simple graphics\n2. Some might not have enough motion/skin to be detected\n3. The min_area might be filtering out some\n\nBut 2-3 people is much better than 52 false positives!Let me now update the VideoProcessor to warm up the detector with 20-30 frames before starting detection. This will give the background model time to initialize.Also, I need to restart the backend with the new detector code.","thinkingSignature":"29b105f7fd3af6b6ee2041b304c81a201228cdcd854689969ecad8ec385a7b9d"},{"type":"text","text":"Tốt hơn nhiều — 2 người thay vì 52! Giờ restart backend với thuật toán mới:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_aw5xwu7atfol_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"kill $(ps aux | grep \"python3 app.py\" | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2}') 2>/dev/null\nsleep 2\n\ncd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/backend && \\\nMONGO_URI=\"mongodb://localhost:27017\" MONGO_DB=\"ppe_safety\" DEBUG=\"false\" FPS_TARGET=\"2\" \\\npython3 app.py > /tmp/s1-backend.log 2>&1 &\necho \"Backend PID: $!\"\nsleep 5\ncurl -s http://localhost:5000/api/summary | python3 -c \"\nimport sys,json\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\nsm=d.get('summary',{})\nprint(f'Detections: {sm}')\nprint(f'Total: {sm.get(\\\"total_persons\\\",0)}')\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":87,"output":385,"cacheRead":118680,"cacheWrite":1699,"totalTokens":120851,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776795475774,"responseId":"0636f255468a74989b65669acef1023d"}}
