{"type":"message","id":"0e2e1347","parentId":"d042333b","timestamp":"2026-04-21T18:20:50.844Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying:\n1. Uploaded video is laggy\n2. Analysis hasn't been completed yet\n\nThe issue is likely:\n1. When a user uploads a video, the backend starts a NEW VideoProcessor with the uploaded video\n2. The VideoProcessor's FPS is set to FPS_TARGET=2 (from env), which should be fine\n3. BUT - the VideoProcessor starts from frame 0 of the uploaded video and needs to build up the MOG2 background model FIRST before detections become accurate\n\nAlso, the backend might be slow to process the video. Let me check if there's an issue with the VideoProcessor or if it's just taking time.\n\n\nThe real problem is that the background subtraction algorithm needs 20-40 frames to build a proper background model before it can start detecting people accurately, which creates a significant delay for uploaded videos. I should test the VideoProcessor directly to see how long this initialization takes and whether that's the bottleneck.\n\nLooking at the timing constraints, 2 FPS with MOG2 and skin detection should handle 720p video without issue on a modern CPU, so the bottleneck is likely just the warm-up period rather than actual performance. The frontend shows a \"connecting camera\" message because the `/api/frame` endpoint isn't returning annotated frames yet—either the processor hasn't finished processing the first frame or the endpoint itself isn't working properly. I need to add a test of the `/api/frame` endpoint to see what's happening, then consider adding a visual loading indicator or processing status to the frontend while detection runs. I think the real issue might be that the `/api/frame` endpoint isn't returning anything while the processor is warming up, so the AnnotatedFrame component is stuck showing the loading state. Let me check the VideoProcessor implementation to see how it's actually feeding frames to the API.","thinkingSignature":"86bfeb0fdcbf416b429cd140ea703f03f8862e5aa55a701c9e880839d2bceb82"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_40l0a50i81xs_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"def /api/frame\\|def get_latest\\|latest_frame\\|annotated_frame\\|frame_count\\|@app.route.*frame\" \\\n  /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/backend/app.py | head -15","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":456,"cacheRead":117358,"cacheWrite":950,"totalTokens":118764,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776795634706,"responseId":"0636f2f454c631059c89e534c3e5d0c9"}}
