{"type":"message","id":"6079ed08","parentId":"5d5e2611","timestamp":"2026-04-21T18:24:34.986Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so:1. Skin pixels: only 713 (0.08%) — very few skin pixels detected\n2. Edge pixels: 17.2% — good edge coverage\n3. Foreground: 0% — MOG2 says no foreground at all\n\nThe issue is that MOG2 doesn't detect any foreground, which means either:\n1. The people in the video are standing still (no motion)\n2. The people are too small to register as foreground\n\nLet me check the frame visually. Let me also try the skin-based approach without MOG2.","thinkingSignature":"074e64b3ab2f21be68f2287f01a065e3b308a3e02e27966762dc30e9c6cb8b51"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_52mgvjxjkl29_1","name":"image","arguments":{"prompt":"Describe this image briefly","image":"/tmp/frame_50_720p.jpg"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":109,"output":166,"cacheRead":128478,"cacheWrite":1218,"totalTokens":129971,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776795867749,"responseId":"0636f3dd7d2328574c1d3bd1318844f3"}}
