{"type":"message","id":"4cbe51c2","parentId":"2eac69df","timestamp":"2026-04-21T18:39:42.638Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me remove that weird `{backend,frontend,devops}` file and also update the README with proper project description.","thinkingSignature":"f1f47ad0224336179740a3d441c1fea13cb01147bd2ded954be100f2a0303f4d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_y6toc8o5hozq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety\n\n# Remove weird file\nrm -f ./{backend,frontend,devops}\n\n# Update README\ncat > README.md << 'EOF'\n# S1 PPE Safety Monitoring System\n## AI Giám sát An toàn Lao động\n\nHệ thống giám sát PPE (Personal Protective Equipment) cho công trường xây dựng bằng Computer Vision.\n\n### Tính năng\n\n- **Nhận diện thời gian thực** mũ bảo hộ và áo phản quang\n- **Hỗ trợ nhiều nguồn video**: Upload file, Camera/Webcam, Video demo\n- **Cảnh báo tức thì** khi phát hiện vi phạm PPE\n- **Dashboard trực quan** với thống kê compliance\n- **Lưu lịch sử cảnh báo** vào MongoDB\n\n### Kiến trúc\n\n```\n├── frontend/          # React + Vite + Ant Design dashboard\n├── backend/          # Flask + Socket.IO + OpenCV PPE detector\n├── devops/           # Docker configuration\n└── README.md\n```\n\n### Công nghệ\n\n- **Frontend**: React 18, Vite, Ant Design, Socket.IO Client\n- **Backend**: Flask, Flask-SocketIO, OpenCV (Haar Cascade + Color Analysis)\n- **Database**: MongoDB\n- **Detection**: Edge+Blob+Color analysis + OpenCV Haar Cascades\n\n### Cài đặt\n\n**Backend:**\n```bash\ncd backend\npip install -r requirements.txt\npython app.py\n```\n\n**Frontend:**\n```bash\ncd frontend\nnpm install\nnpm run dev\n```\n\n**Docker:**\n```bash\ncd devops\ndocker-compose up -d\n```\n\n### API Endpoints\n\n- `GET /api/summary` — Latest detection summary\n- `GET /api/frame` — Latest annotated frame (JPEG)\n- `GET /api/alerts` — Recent violation alerts\n- `POST /api/upload-video` — Upload video for analysis\n- `POST /api/detect-frame` — Detect PPE in a single frame\n\n### License\n\nMIT\nEOF\n\necho \"README updated\"\n\n# Add all files\ngit add -A\ngit status --short | head -20","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":255,"output":588,"cacheRead":146433,"cacheWrite":826,"totalTokens":148102,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776796771056,"responseId":"0636f76465388bffe3f7358ef379ca6e"}}
