{"type":"message","id":"148b856c","parentId":"f0b5fc82","timestamp":"2026-04-21T18:43:51.138Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, the main project is only 2.7MB after cleanup. The disk space issue is not from the PPE project. The disk is 99% full regardless. That's a system-level issue - the VPS is nearly out of disk space.\n\nFor production, I should:1. Create a proper production-ready setup\n2. Set up environment variables properly3. Add a health check endpoint\n4. Create a proper Dockerfile/docker-compose5. Set up the frontend for production build6. Document everything\n\nLet me focus on what I can do for production readiness. I'll:\n1. Update .gitignore to exclude all unnecessary files\n2. Create a proper docker-compose.yml for production3. \n\nNow I'm going to add environment configuration files and set up health checks to round out the production readiness.","thinkingSignature":"fdee994c791ef149cf525b601488dc14a4f54ea4619ebdca74f46f6c21a52225"},{"type":"text","text":"Project chỉ 2.7MB. Disk full là vấn đề VPS (34GB disk). Giờ tập trung vào **hoàn thiện production**:\n\n**Bước 1: Cập nhật `.gitignore` và loại bỏ files thừa:**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3culzhovi7in_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/.gitignore","content":"# Dependencies\nnode_modules/\ndist/\nbuild/\n.env\n\n# Python\n__pycache__/\n*.pyc\nvenv/\n.venv/\n*.egg-info/\n\n# Uploaded videos (user content)\nfrontend/public/video/uploaded_*\n\n# Logs\n*.log\nnpm-debug.log*\nyarn-debug.log*\nyarn-error.log*\n\n# OS\n.DS_Store\nThumbs.db\n\n# IDE\n.vscode/\n.idea/\n*.swp\n*.swo\n\n# Git\n.git/\n\n# Temp\n*.tmp\n*.bak\n*.orig\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":129,"output":398,"cacheRead":151840,"cacheWrite":474,"totalTokens":152841,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","times