{"type":"message","id":"492e0c4f","parentId":"f2fe61fd","timestamp":"2026-04-21T18:45:17.135Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me update the main README with production deployment instructions and project overview.","thinkingSignature":"42799fed92f3e0f8c9efa620eed6bbe579b9ab598d385997e283cec0747750f4"},{"type":"text","text":"**Bước 9: Cập nhật README với hướng dẫn production:**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c00tenappyik_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/README.md","content":"# S1 PPE Safety Monitoring System\n### AI Giám sát An toàn Lao động\n\nHệ thống giám sát **PPE (Personal Protective Equipment)** cho công trường xây dựng bằng Computer Vision. Phát hiện real-time mũ bảo hộ và áo phản quang.\n\n---\n\n## 🏗 Kiến trúc\n\n```\n┌──────────────┐     WebSocket      ┌──────────────┐\n│   Browser    │◄─────────────────►│    Backend    │\n│  (Dashboard) │   HTTP/REST       │  (Flask)      │\n│  React+Vite  │◄─────────────────►│  OpenCV       │\n└──────────────┘                   │  PPE Detector │\n       │                           └──────┬───────┘\n       │                                  │\n   Port 3000                         Port 5000\n                                    ┌──────▼───────┐\n                                    │   MongoDB    │\n                                    └──────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 Triển khai nhanh\n\n### Cách 1: Docker (Khuyến nghị cho Production)\n\n```bash\ncd devops\ndocker-compose up -d\n# Truy cập: http://localhost:3003\n```\n\n### Cách 2: Manual Setup\n\n**Backend:**\n```bash\ncd backend\ncp .env.example .env\n# Chỉnh sửa .env nếu cần\npip install -r requirements.txt\npython app.py\n```\n\n**Frontend:**\n```bash\ncd frontend\nnpm install\nnpm run dev\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📁 Cấu trúc Project\n\n```\ns1-ppe-safety-monitoring/\n├── backend/\n│   ├── app.py              # Flask REST API + Socket.IO server\n│   ├── detector.py         # PPE detection engine (Haar Cascade + Color)\n│   ├── video_processor.py  # Video frame processor\n│   ├── requirements.txt    # Python dependencies\n│   ├── .env.example       # Environment variables template\n│   └── Dockerfile.backend  # Production Docker image\n│\n├── frontend/\n│   ├── src/\n│   │   ├── App.jsx        # Main dashboard (React)\n│   │   └── main.jsx       # Entry point\n│   ├── public/video/      # Demo video & uploads\n│   ├── vite.config.js     # Vite + proxy config\n│   └── package.json\n│\n├── devops/\n│   ├── docker-compose.yml # Docker deployment\n│   ├── Dockerfile.backend\n│   └── start.sh           # Quick startup script\n│\n├── README.md\n└── .gitignore\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔌 API Endpoints\n\n| Method | Endpoint | Mô tả |\n|--------|----------|--------|\n| `GET` | `/health` | Health check |\n| `GET` | `/api/summary` | Latest detection summary |\n| `GET` | `/api/frame` | Latest annotated frame (JPEG) |\n| `GET` | `/api/alerts` | Recent violation alerts |\n| `POST` | `/api/upload-video` | Upload video for analysis |\n| `POST` | `/api/detect-frame` | Detect PPE in a single frame (base64/image) |\n\n### WebSocket Events (Socket.IO)\n\n**Subscribe:**\n```js\nsocket.emit('subscribe', { camera_id: 'camera-1' })\n```\n\n**Receive:**\n- `detection_summary` — Updated summary every frame\n- `ppe_alert` — Violation alert when detected\n\n---\n\n## ⚙ Cấu hình\n\nTạo file `backend/.env`:\n\n```bash\n# MongoDB\nMONGO_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017\nMONGO_DB=ppe_safety\n\n# Server\nPORT=5000\nDEBUG=false\n\n# Detection\nFPS_TARGET=2        # FPS xử lý (1-5, cao hơn = nhiều CPU hơn)\nVIDEO_PATH=demo.mp4\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎥 Nguồn Video\n\n- **Video Demo**: Video construction site có sẵn\n- **Tải Video**: Upload file MP4/AVI từ máy tính\n- **Camera**: Sử dụng webcam để detect real-time\n\n---\n\n## 🛠 Công nghệ\n\n| Layer | Tech |\n|-------|------|\n| Dashboard | React 18, Vite, Ant Design |\n| Backend API | Flask, Flask-SocketIO |\n| Detection | OpenCV (Haar Cascade + HSV Color Analysis) |\n| Database | MongoDB |\n| Container | Docker, Docker Compose |\n\n---\n\n## ⚠ Lưu ý Production\n\n1. **Disk**: Đảm bảo đủ dung lượng cho video uploads\n2. **MongoDB**: Kết nối từ `.env` — không dùng localhost nếu deploy trên cloud\n3. **HTTPS**: Nên dùng Nginx/Cloudflare proxy phía trước\n4. **Video Format**: Khuyến nghị H.264 MP4, ≤ 1080p cho hiệu năng tốt nhất\n\n---\n\n## 📄 License\n\nMIT\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":74,"output":1213,"cacheRead":154684,"cacheWrite":1234,"totalTokens":157205,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776797096867,"responseId":"0636f8aa69db4518565511c1f5bb3776"}}
