{"type":"message","id":"e41be084","parentId":"df51960b","timestamp":"2026-04-21T18:46:40.058Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, both commits are there. The project is pushed. Let me summarize everything that was done for production.","thinkingSignature":"4cf073d67f65a85b7518bec3d9eb69a4c8dd8a2a613fa918ffa4005a62922a80"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Hoàn tất Production!**\n\n**GitLab:** https://gitlab.com/pet-connect2/s1-ppe-safety-monitoring\n\n**2 commits:**\n1. `feat: S1 PPE Safety Monitoring System` — code ban đầu\n2. `prod: production-ready infrastructure` — production infrastructure\n\n---\n\n### 🏭 Production có gì\n\n| Component | Chi tiết |\n|-----------|---------|\n| **Docker Compose** | MongoDB + Backend + Frontend tự động |\n| **Docker Backend** | Gunicorn workers, health check, multi-stage |\n| **Nginx Config** | HTTPS proxy, video streaming, cache headers |\n| **Startup Script** | `./start.sh` — install + run tự động |\n| **Environment** | `.env.example` — tất cả config variables |\n| **README** | Hướng dẫn deploy đầy đủ |\n\n### 🚀 Deploy nhanh\n\n```bash\n# Clone\ngit clone https://gitlab.com/pet-connect2/s1-ppe-safety-monitoring.git\ncd s1-ppe-safety-monitoring\n\n# Docker (1 lệnh)\ncd devops && docker-compose up -d\n\n# Hoặc manual\n./devops/start.sh\n```\n\n### 📋 Còn cần làm thêm cho production thực sự\n\n1. **HTTPS** — Cấu hình SSL certificate (Let's Encrypt)\n2. **Domain** — Point domain về VPS\n3. **MongoDB URI** — Thay bằng MongoDB Atlas hoặc server thật\n4. **Video upload limit** — Cấu hình nginx `client_max_body_size`\n5. **CI/CD** — GitLab CI để auto-deploy"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":121,"output":401,"cacheRead":159219,"cacheWrite":613,"totalTokens":160354,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776797189752,"responseId":"0636f907ff77297a12731fb0df06cd70"}}
