{"type":"message","id":"b6eec1bf","parentId":"bf497176","timestamp":"2026-04-21T18:47:57.970Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to continue developing the project with full features, not just production setup. Let me think about what features are still needed:\n\n1. **Better PPE detection accuracy** - The current algorithm using Haar cascades isn't very accurate\n2. **Better video handling** - The video processing is still slow for 4K\n3. **Better UI** - The dashboard could be improved\n4. **Real-time webcam detection** - Currently the webcam mode sends frames to backend but it's slow\n5. **Video playback synchronization** - The annotated frame and video should be synchronized\n6. **Export reports** - PDF/CSV reports\n7. **Multiple cameras support**\n8. **User authentication**\n\n\n9. **Alert history and filtering**\n10. **Better alert sounds**\n\nLet me clarify with the user what they want to prioritize, but first I should look at the current system status to understand what's already working and what needs the most attention. Let me re-read the SOUL.md and USER.md to understand the context better.\n\nActually, I should just ask what features matter most to them and suggest some options rather than listing everything.","thinkingSignature":"6334347eab40c3f0c09aab9ff487a78cba67b277ba3a79dc5207c4628d6086e0"},{"type":"text","text":"Được rồi! Trước khi tiếp tục, hỏi bạn vài câu để ưu tiên đúng:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_46ngr8b3x1p0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check current state\ncurl -s http://localhost:5000/api/summary | python3 -c \"\nimport sys,json\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\nsm=d.get('summary',{})\nprint('Backend:', sm)\n\"\ncurl -s -o /dev/null -w \"Frontend: %{http_code}\\n\" http://localhost:3003","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":379,"cacheRead":158613,"cacheWrite":724,"totalTokens":159716,"co